WOMEN, OLD PEOPLE AND CHILDREN, ARE ON THE MOVE 
TOWARDS THE SLAVONIAN MOUNTAINS AND BANJA LUKA. 
 
9.  APART FROM THAT, A PROCLAMATION FOR FORCED EXODUS 
 
 
