-- CROATIAN ARMY REPORT (ROUGH CONSULATE TRANSLATION) 
 
12.  BEGIN TEXT.  ALREADY FOR A LONGER PERIOD OF 
TIME, SINCE THE AGGRESSION ON THE CROATIAN REPUBLIC 
BEGAN, JNA ENEMY FORCES AND CHETNIK UNITS ARE TRYING 
TO ACHIEVE THEIR IMPERIALIST GOAL OF \"GREAT SERBIA\". 
NOW THEY ARE TRYING TO REALIZE THIS IRRATIONAL GOAL 
CONFIRM THOUSANDS OF HURT CIVILIANS, DESTROYED 
CROATIAN VILLAGES AND TOWNS.  CHILDREN, WOMEN, 
WOUNDED, OLD AND FEEBLE ARE NOT SPARED FROM THE WAR 
SUFFERINGS CAUSED BY THE OCCUPYING FORCES. 
WP                                                       U 
UNCLASSIFIED 
 
SIPDIS 
 
HOSPITALS, CHURCHES, KINDERGARTEN SCHOOLS, OLD FOLKS 
HOMES, OBJECTS OF ZERO CATEGORY, ETC., ARE DESTROYED. 
 
13.  ONE OF THE MANY DAMAGED PLACES IS GRUBISNO POLJE 
WHICH FOR A LONG PERIOD OF TIME HAS BEEN EXPOSED TO 
ENEMY MILITARY ACTION.  ATTACKS FROM THE AIR AND 
MORTAR SHELLS THREATENED IN ADDITION TO THE TOWN ALSO 
CROATIAN VILLAGES IN THE AREA AND IN ADDITION TO THE 
SUFFERINGS OF CIVILIANS, GREAT MATERIAL DAMAGE WAS 
DONE. 
 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
PAGE 04        ZAGREB  01569  03 OF 04  071629Z 
