TO CREATE MISUNDERSTANDING, IN ORDER, UNDER THE 
PRESSURE OF THE WORLD PUBLICITY, TO TRY TO PREVENT 
MILITARY ACTION OF THE CROATIAN ARMY FROM THE 
LIBERATION OF ITS OWN TERRITORY, AND TO JUSTIFY ITS 
OWN IMPERIALIST ACTIVITY. 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  01569  04 OF 04  071629Z 
 
