BENKOVAC AND KNIN.  THEY WOULD LIKE TO INVESTIGATE 
ON THE SPOT WAR CRIMES AND HUMAN RIGHTS VIOLATIONS 
OF CITIZENS OF CROATIAN NATIONALITY.  THEY WOULD 
 
 
