TUDJMAN: FORWARD TO A DEMOCRATIC FUTURE, WITH A 
LITTLE HELP FROM FRIENDS 
--------------------------------------------- -------- 
 
17.  CRITICS OF THE CURRENT GOVERNMENT--HUMAN RIGHTS 
ACTIVISTS, OPPOSITION POLITICAL FIGURES, SERBIAN 
LEADERS AND OTHERS--ALL AGREE THAT IN THE SHORT TERM, 
ABSENT A DRAMATIC TURN OF EVENTS, PRESIDENT FRANJO 
TUDJMAN WILL COMFORTABLY WIN ANOTHER TERM AS 
PRESIDENT, WHICH UNDER THE NEW ELECTION LAW WILL BE A 
FIVE-YEAR TERM.  IN SPITE OF THE CROATIAN PRESIDENT\'S 
AUTHORITARIAN STYLE OF GOVERNING, MANY SEE HIS 
RE-ELECTION AS THE BEST OUTCOME OF AN ELECTION THAT 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  00527  06 OF 07  091307Z 
COULD MOVE CROATIA DANGEROUSLY TO THE RIGHT. .CALLING 
TUDJMAN THE BEST ALTERNATIVE OF A BAD LOT WOULD HAVE 
BEEN UNTHINKABLE ONLY MONTHS AGO, BUT SUCH HAS BEEN 
THE EFFECT OF THE VIOLENCE AND FIGHTING ON THE 
CROATIAN NATION. 
 
18.  UNLIKE SLOVENIA, THE INFLUENCE OF THE U.S. IS 
TANGIBLE AND PERVASIVE.  WITH THOUSANDS OF AMCITS OF 
CROATIAN DESCENT ACTIVELY SUPPORTING CROATIAN 
INDEPENDENCE AND TRAVELLING BACK AND FORTH, U.S. 
INTERESTS CUT ACROSS ECONOMIC, SOCIAL, CULTURAL AND 
FAMILY CONNECTIONS.  FROM ACROSS THE SPECTRUM IN 
CROATIAN SOCIETY, THE WORKING ASSUMPTION IS THAT THE 
U.S. WILL INEVITABLY PLAY A LEADING ROLE IN THE 
TRANSFORMATION OF THE REPUBLIC.  IN OUR OPINION, THAT 
IS THE ULTIMATE HOPE OF THOSE WHO DOUBT THE MOTIVES 
AND INTENTIONS OF THE TUDJMAN GOVERNMENT. 
- 
U.S. - CROATIAN RELATIONS 
------------------------- 
 
19.  EVEN MORE THAN WITH SLOVENIA, CROATS ARE 
DEMONSTRABLY MORE RECEPTIVE TO THE BROADEST AND 
CLOSEST OF DIPLOMATIC RELATIONS.  FOR THE U.S., 
CROATIA IS OF SIGNIFICANCE ASIDE FROM OUR INTEREST IN 
LIMITING THE DANGER OF CONFLICT ARISING FROM 
CROATIA\'S ENTANGLED RELATIONS WITH SERBIA.  WITH A 
STRONG, ACTIVE EMIGRE COMMUNITY IN THE U.S., CROATIA 
WILL BE A MAJOR TARGET OF U.S. INVESTMENT AND 
POLITICAL INTEREST.  IT ATTRACTS TENS OF THOUSANDS OF 
AMCIT TOURISTS TO ITS RESORTS ALONG THE DALMATIAN 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
PAGE 04        ZAGREB  00527  06 OF 07  091307Z 
COAST.  PEOPLE TO PEOPLE EXCHANGES WILL BE RESTORED 
AND GROW EXPONENTIALLY OVER THE YEARS.  ITS LOCATION 
AND COASTAL POSITION MEAN CROATIA WILL PLAY SOME ROLE 
IN THE GROWTH OF CENTRAL EUROPE. 
 
 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
