USUN PLEASE PASS TO SYG\'S SPECIAL ENVOY, CYRUS VANCE 
 
E.O. 12356: N/A 
TAGS:  PREL, YO 
SUBJECT: CROATIAN PRESIDENT FRANJO TUDJMAN\'S LETTER TO 
