REFUGEES FROM THE VILLAGTE OF MIKLUSEVCI ARRIVED IN 
VINKOVCI.  THE REFUGEES ARE OF RUTHENIAN 
NATIONALITY.  I WISH TO REMIND YOU THAT IT IS A 
 
 
