OGULIN:  STILL IN A STATE OF WAR 
-------------------------------- 
 
9.  WHATEVER HOPE WE BROUGHT WITH US FROM VRBOVSKO 
WAS DASHED UPON ENTRY INTO OGULIN (LIKE VRBOVSKO 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  00954  05 OF 08  111239Z 
DISTRICT ABOUT 65 PERCENT CROAT AND 35 PERCENT SERB), 
A CITY UNCOMFORTABLY CLOSE TO THE FRONT LINES THAT 
HAS HAD AN ENTIRELY DIFFERENT WAR EXPERIENCE.  IN A 
SPACE OF LESS THAN 30 KILOMETERS, WE HAD GONE FROM A 
POTENTIAL MODEL OF POST-WAR SERB/CROAT RELATIONS TO 
AN AREA THAT EXHIBITS ALL THE REASONS WHY SERBS AND 
CROATS IN THESE REGIONS MAY NEVER AGAIN TURN THEIR 
BACKS ON ONE ANOTHER.  THE MEETING, A TIGHTLY WOUND 
AFFAIR, INCLUDED DISPLACED PERSONS FROM A DESTROYED, 
KRAJINA-CONTROLLED, ONCE PREDOMINANTLY CROAT TOWN, 
OGULIN DISTRICT OFFICIALS, AND \"LOYAL\" SERB 
CITIZENS.  THE TENSION BETWEEN SERBS AND CROATS IN 
THIS MEETING (14 PARTICIPANTS) IN THE OGULIN DISTRICT 
HALL WAS PALPABLE. 
- 
10.  A LOT OF THE TENSION COMES FROM OGULIN\'S 
WAR-TIME EXPERIENCE.  A JNA BARRACKS WAS LOCATED IN 
THE CENTER OF THE CITY OF OGULIN, NEXT DOOR TO THE 
DISTRICT HALL.  CONSIDERABLE FIGHTING TOOK PLACE IN 
THE CITY BEFORE THE JNA ABANDONED THE SITE.  IN 
ADDITION, THE CITY IS LOCATED ONLY 15 KM FROM THE 
FRONT LINE AND SOME OF THE OGULIN DISTRICT REMAINS 
UNDER THE CONTROL OF KRAJINA FORCES (BUT OUTSIDE THE 
UNPAS, AS LOCAL OFFICIALS ARE QUICK TO POINT OUT). 
ADDITIONALLY, THOUGH THERE ARE NO CONCRETE FIGURES, 
MANY SERBS LEFT OGULIN BEFORE AND DURING THE WAR, 
LEAVING A BAD TASTE AMONG MANY CROATS WHO BELIEVE 
THAT THEY ALL LEFT TO FIGHT FOR THE \"CHETNIKS\" 
AGAINST THEIR OLD NEIGHBORS.  SABORSKO (THE CROATIAN 
TOWN REFERRED TO IN PARA 9) RESIDENTS, EMBITTERED BY 
THE DESTRUCTION OF THEIR VILLAGE, IN WHICH THEY CLAIM 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
PAGE 04        ZAGREB  00954  05 OF 08  111239Z 
55 OF THE 1,600 PRE-WAR POPULATION WERE KILLED, 
ARGUED THAT JUSTICE MUST BE DONE TO THOSE SERBS 
RESPONSIBLE.  AND THEY SAY THEY PERSONALLY KNOW THE 
 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
