E.O. 12356: N/A 
TAGS:  PGOV, PREL, PINR, MOPS, BI, HR 
SUBJECT:  CROATIAN PRESS ON THE DUBROVNIK FRONT, 
TREBINJE AND CROATIAN FORCES IN BOSNIA. 
 
CANNON FIRE HAS BEEN OPENED AT DUBROVNIK\'S SUBURBS 
MOKOSICA AND OTHER PLACES OF THE RIJEKA DUBROVACKA. 
CHETNIKS HAVE FORTIFIED THEMSELVES ON IVANICA AND 
USKOPOLJE, LOCATED AT THE STATE BORDER.  THE LITTORAL 
BELT AT THE EXTREME SOUTH PART OF CROATIA IS VERY 
NARROW AND THE AREA BETWEEN SREBRENO AND MLINI IS NOT 
EVEN THREE KILOMETERS FROM THE COAST TO THE              . 
INTERSTATE BORDER.  AN ATTEMPT BY TREBINJE CHETNIKS 
TO BREAKTHROUGH ACROSS IVANICA COULD BE EASILY 
REPELLED BY THE CROATIAN FORCES WITH THE OPENING OF 
FIRE FROM BRGAT, ZARKOVICA AND DUBAC.  BREAKTHROUGHS 
CAN BE ALSO EXPECTED ACROSS THE VISOCNIK SADDLE, 
LOWER SLOPES OF SNJEZNICA AND THE JAVOR PASS. 
 
STILL THERE IS AN EFFECTIVE SOLUTION FOR THE 
NEUTRALIZATION OF THE PRESSURE FROM TREBINJE.  HVO 
(CROATIAN DEFENSE COUNCIL) FIGHTERS, WHO WITH THEIR 
BREAKTHROUGH TO NEUM HAVE PRACTICALLY LIBERATED THE 
WHOLE TERRITORY OF THE BOSNIAN-HERCEGOVIAN COMMUNITY 
RAVNO, SHOULD NOT CONSIDER THAT THEIR FINAL GOAL HAS 
BEEN ACHIEVED.  THE TREBINJE TRUCK DRIVER WILL NOT BE 
EASILY RECONCILED WITH THE LOSS OF ONE PART OF HIS 
PLANNED DUKEDOM AND THEREFORE HE WILL CONTINUE TO 
ATTACK RAVNO.  THE ONLY WAY TO GIVE A DESERVED 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  01002  02 OF 02  171305Z 
LECTURE TO VUCUREVIC FOR ALL HIS COMMITTED CRIMES 
AGAINST THE CROATIAN AND MUSLIM NATIONS, IS A FIRM 
CONTINUATION OF A BREAKTHROUGH UNDERTAKEN BY THE HVO 
TO POPOVO POLJE AND THE LIBERATION OF TREBINJE FROM 
CHETNIKS.  OBJECTIONS OF THE BELGRADE-PODGORICA 
AGGRESSORS CONCERNING CROATIAN COMPLICITY IN THE WAR 
ON THE B-H TERRITORY, HAVE BEEN DROPPED.  INFLUENTIAL 
INTERNATIONAL POLITICAL CIRCLES HAVE RECOGNIZED THE 
HVO AS A SPONTANEOUS RESISTANCE OF THE CROATIAN 
NATION IN B-H AGAINST THE SERBIAN MONTENEGRIN 
AGGRESSION.  HVO FORCES HAVE RECOGNIZED B-H AND THEY 
FIGHT FOR THIS STATE IN THE SAME WAY AS THE B-H 
TERRITORIAL DEFENSE WITH WHICH THEY WILL CREATE IN 
THE NEAREST FUTURE A B-H ARMY. 
 
END TEXT. 
 
EINIK 
 
 
 
