THE CROATIAN ARMY WHO ARE CITIZENS OF B-H HAD 
RETURNED TO DEFEND THEIR HOMETOWNS.  THE MINISTRY 
INVITED INTERESTED JOURNALISTS TO INVESTIGATE THIS 
MATTER WITH THE MINISTRY\'S ASSISTANCE.   LOCAL 
