SUBJECT:  ZAGREB UPDATE:  JUNE 24, 1992 
 
 
6.  ZAGREB\'S OFFICIAL CASUALTY FIGURES FOR THE PERIOD 
AUGUST 15, 1990 THROUGH JUNE 23, 1992, INCLUDE: 3,861 
KILLED AND 20,127 INJURED.  AMONG THE DEAD ARE 1,773 
CIVILIANS AND 1,389 MEMBERS OF THE CROATIAN ARMED 
FORCES. 
 
