SERBIAN ORTHODOX BISHOP IN BOSNIA GAVE TO BELGRADE\'S 
INDEPENDENT TV STUDIO \"B\" IN WHICH HE ALLEGED HE 
MURDERS OF 120,000 MUSLIMS IN B-H, THE DESTRUCTION 
OF 200 MOSQUES, AND THE SERBIAN RAPE AND 
IMPREGNATION OF 30,000 MUSLIM WOMEN.  THE BISHOP 
 
 
