-         -- ANOTHER GRIM REPORT FROM SECTOR EAST 
 
QUICKLY FREED.  ONE SERB REPORTEDLY WAS ARRESTED FOR 
THREE CONSECUTIVE MURDERS.  HE WAS RELEASED TWICE 
WITHOUT PUNISHMENT.  AFTER THE THIRD ARREST HE WAS 
TAKEN TO THE SERBIAN BORDER AND ALLOWED TO CROSS INTO 
VOJVODINA.  DURING THE NIGHT OF SEPTEMBER 7-8, A 
NON-SERB COUPLE WAS MURDERED IN THE UNPA.  THERE ARE 
NO SUSPECTS.  ON OCTOBER 1, TWO MUSLIMS WERE MURDERED 
IN THE UNPA.  THERE ARE NO SUSPECTS.  MILAN ILICH, 
\"PRESIDENT\" OF THE VUKOVAR REGION EXECUTIVE COUNCIL, 
WAS ASKED IN OCTOBER WHY NO ACTION HAD BEEN TAKEN 
AGAINST KNOWN TERRORISTS.  HE REPORTEDLY RESPONDED 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  01962  04 OF 08  091325Z 
SIMPLY THAT, WHILE HE OPPOSED THE METHODS USED TO 
DRIVE NON-SERBS, HE DID NOT QUARREL WITH THE RESULTS. 
 
13.  UNPROFOR REPORTEDLY INFORMED ILICH OF AN 
ESPECIALLY EGREGIOUS TERRORIZATION OF A NUMBER OF 
ELDERLY NON-SERB WOMEN WHO WERE FINALLY DRIVEN OUT OF 
THEIR HOMES IN SEPTEMBER.  AFTER A DELAY, DURING 
WHICH HE WAS SUPPOSED TO BE INVESTIGATING THE CASE, 
ILICH SENT A REQUEST THAT THE WOMEN SIGN OVER THEIR 
PROPERTY TO THE KRAJINA AND CONFIRM THAT THEY WERE 
LEAVING \"VOLUNTARILY.\" 
 
-------------------- 
BLAMING THE REFUGEES 
-------------------- 
 
14.  ILICH TOLD THE CSCE DELEGATION THAT THE REGION 
HAS TAKEN IN A NUMBER OF SERBIAN REFUGEES FROM 
BOSNIA-HERCEGOVINA AND ELSEWHERE.  HE CLAIMED THAT 
\"THOSE PEOPLE (SERBS) WHO HAVE LOST EVERYTHING ON THE 
OTHER SIDE ACT IN AN EMOTIONAL WAY.\"  THESE PEOPLE 
OFTEN CAUSE \"DIFFICULTIES,\" HE CLAIMED. 
 
15.  UN OBSERVERS, HOWEVER, TELL A DIFFERENT STORY. 
WHILE ACKNOWLEDGING THAT THE INFLUX OF SERBIAN 
REFUGEES, ESTIMATED AT SOME 47,000, HAS AGGRAVATED A 
TENSE SITUATION, UN CIVILIAN POLICE FAMILIAR WITH 
DAILY CONDITIONS BELIEVE THAT MANY CRIMINALS COME NOT 
FROM REFUGEE RANKS BUT FROM OFFICIALDOM.  THEY CITED . 
MEMBERS OF THE CIVILIAN ADMINISTRATION, SUCH AS THE 
\"MAYOR\" OF THE TOWN OF DALJ, S. DORGJA (AKA \"BRIGA\"), 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
PAGE 04        ZAGREB  01962  04 OF 08  091325Z 
WHO HAS BEEN SEEN THREATENING, BEATING, AND SHOOTING 
AROUND PERSONAL RESIDENCES IN AN EFFORT TO INTIMIDATE 
NON-SERBS INTO LEAVING.  IN THIS CONTEXT, UNPROFOR 
 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
