-         -- ANOTHER GRIM REPORT FROM SECTOR EAST 
 
UN RELEASE SERBIAN ARMORED CARS IMPOUNDED BY THE UN 
SO THAT THEY COULD \"FIGHT CRIME IN THE VILLAGES.\" 
 
------------------------------ 
ARKAN AND OTHER PARAMILITARIES 
------------------------------ 
 
19.  THE NOTORIOUS SERBIAN TERRORIST ARKAN HAS BEEN 
SEEN AGAIN IN THE UNPA.  HE WAS REPORTEDLY FETED AS A 
GUEST SPEAKER AT A RECENT PARTY IN THE REGION.  THE 
COMPOUND AND TRAINING COMPLEX AT ERDUT NEXT TO UN 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  01962  06 OF 08  091326Z 
HEADQUARTERS HAS A NEW HIGH RED BRICK WALL AROUND 
PART OF THE PERIMETER.  HIS MEN REPORTEDLY HAVE 
BECOME MEMBERS OF THE \"POLICE.\"  THE SERBIAN \"RED 
BERETS,\" WHO HAVE BEEN ACCUSED OF WAR CRIMES IN ILOK 
AND SEVERAL OTHER VILLAGES, HAVE MOVED TO THE 
SOUTHERN PART OF THE UNPA AND THEIR MEMBERS ARE NOW 
SEEN IN SERBIAN \"SPECIAL POLICE\" UNIFORMS. 
 
20.  A SO-CALLED \"BORDER POLICE\" ALSO IS BEING RUN BY 
THE SERBIAN SIDE.  THESE INDIVIDUALS HAVE BEEN SEEN 
MANNING CHECKPOINTS WITH REGULAR \"POLICE,\" AND ARE 
REPORTED TO BE INVOLVED IN SOME OF THE WORST VIOLENCE 
AGAINST CIVILIANS.  LOCAL \"POLICE\" HAVE TOLD THEIR 
INTERNATIONAL COUNTERPARTS THAT THEY ARE AFRAID TO 
PURSUE CASES AGAINST THE \"BORDER POLICE\" AND \"SPECIAL 
POLICE\" LEST THEY THEMSELVES BE ATTACKED OR MURDERED. 
IN A HEATED EXCHANGE WITH THE CSCE DELEGATION ON 
OCTOBER 4, THE SERBIAN VUKOVAR AUTHORITIES REFUSED TO 
PROVIDE ANY INFORMATION ON NUMBERS OF THE \"BORDER\" 
AND \"SPECIAL POLICE,\" CLAIMING THAT ONLY THE KNIN 
AUTHORITIES COULD RELEASE THAT DATA. 
 
----------------------------- 
LEGAL HARASSMENT OF NON-SERBS 
----------------------------- 
 
21.  EMBOFFS ALSO HEARD REPORTS FROM CREDIBLE SOURCES 
OF OTHER, MORE SUBTLE FORMS OF HARASSMENT OF NON-SERBS 
IN THE VUKOVAR AREA.  FOR EXAMPLE, UNDER THE GUISE OF 
HELPING THE DISPLACED, A NUMBER OF HUNGARIAN AND 
SLOVAK HOMEOWNERS HAVE BEEN ORDERED TO TAKE IN SERBIAN 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
PAGE 04        ZAGREB  01962  06 OF 08  091326Z 
REFUGEES.  THESE REFUGEES REPORTEDLY HARASS AND 
INTIMIDATE THEIR \"HOSTS\" UNTIL THE LATTER FINALLY 
MOVE OUT, THUS \"ABANDONING\" THE PROPERTY AND MAKING 
 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
