-         -- ANOTHER GRIM REPORT FROM SECTOR EAST 
 
IT AVAILABLE FOR LEGAL TAKEOVER BY THE INTRUDERS. 
 
22.  RELIABLE SOURCES INDICATED THAT THE KRAJINA 
\"GOVERNMENT\" HAS \"LEGISLATION\" BY WHICH FAMILIES MAY 
BE EVICTED IF THEY HAVE RELATIVES WHO HAVE SERVED IN 
THE CROATIAN ARMED FORCES.  IN A HEATED EXCHANGE WITH 
THE CSCE DELEGATION OCTOBER 4, THE VUKOVAR SERBIAN 
DELEGATION DENIED THAT ANY SUCH LEGISLATION EXISTED 
OR THAT SUCH THINGS OCCURRED.  INSTEAD THEY CITED THE 
FORMATION OF THEIR OWN HUMAN RIGHTS COMMISSION TO 
HANDLE SUCH COMPLAINTS. 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  01962  07 OF 08  091326Z 
 
23.  INTERESTED IN THE \"NEWLY FORMED\" VUKOVAR HUMAN 
RIGHTS COMMISSION, THE CSCE DELEGATION INQUIRED ABOUT 
THE GUIDELINES AND INTERNATIONALLY-RECOGNIZED 
CONVENTIONS WHICH THE COMMISSION PRESUMABLY USED TO 
GUIDE ITS WORK.  AFTER AN EMBARRASSINGLY LONG SILENCE, 
THE CHAIRMAN, HEARING NO SUGGESTIONS FROM HIS NINE 
COLLEAGUES AT THE TABLE, MUMBLED, \"WE USE THEM ALL.\" 
IN EMBOFFS\' JUDGMENT, HE DIDN\'T HAVE A CLUE. 
 
24.  ATTACKS HAVE ALSO BEGUN RECENTLY ON MARRIAGES IN 
WHICH ONE OF THE PARTIES IS NON-SERBIAN.  THE  , 
HARASSMENT HAS INCLUDED MAKING A LIST OF SUCH UNIONS 
FOR \"CENSUS\" PURPOSES BUT WITH THE OBVIOUS OBJECTIVE 
OF INTIMIDATING THESE COUPLES. 
 
------------------------- 
THREE ALLEGED MASS GRAVES 
------------------------- 
 
25.  AMONG THE MANY RUMORS CIRCULATING IN SECTOR EAST 
ABOUT MASS MURDERS AND MASS GRAVES, UN SOURCES 
CONSIDER THREE ALLEGED INSTANCES PARTICULARLY 
CREDIBLE.  SOME 70 BODIES ARE BELIEVED TO HAVE BEEN 
BURIED IN ONE LOCATION IN THE GRAVEYARD AT LOVAS. 
THE SITE IS KEPT FREE OF WEEDS AND TENDED BY UNKNOWN 
VISITORS, WHICH SUGGESTS THAT NEIGHBORS ARE AWARE OF 
THE SIGNIFICANCE OF THE LOCATION.  THERE IS A NEWLY 
EXCAVATED AND REFILLED SITE IN FRONT OF THE ROMAN 
CATHOLIC CHURCH AT TORDINCI WHERE SOME 208 ARE 
BELIEVED TO BE BURIED.  THE THIRD LOCATION IS WITHIN 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
PAGE 04        ZAGREB  01962  07 OF 08  091326Z 
A PARK IN THE VILLAGE OF ERNESTINOVO WHERE 30 BODIES 
ARE BELIEVED TO HAVE BEEN INTERRED. 
 
 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
