--------------------------- 
WOMEN\'S QUARTERS AT OMARSKA 
--------------------------- 
 
16. (U)  X. SAID THE THIRTY-EIGHT WOMEN IN THE CAMP 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  02038  06 OF 09  161651Z 
SLEPT IN TWO ROOMS NEAR THE COMMANDER\'S HEADQUARTERS. 
THE ROOM NUMBERS ON THE DOORS WERE 102 AND 103.  MOST 
OF THE WOMEN WERE SINGLE, DIVORCED, OR WIDOWED.  THEY 
SLEPT ON THE FLOOR WITH ONE BLANKET FOR EVERY TWO 
WOMEN.  AS THEY TRIED TO SLEEP, THE WOMEN INVARIABLY 
HEARD THE SCREAMS OF PRISONERS BEING TORTURED NEXT 
DOOR.  THIS WAS THE \"INTERROGATION\" ROOM.  EACH 
MORNING THE WOMEN WERE WOKEN UP AT SIX, AND TWO WERE 
CHOSEN RANDOMLY TO CLEAN THE \"INTERROGATION\" ROOM. 
IT WAS COVERED WITH FRESH BLOOD EACH MORNING.  THE 
\"INTERROGATION\" ROOM HAD THREE TABLES PUSHED AGAINST 
THE WALLS, AND WHIPS MADE FROM HEAVY WIRE CABLE. 
UNDER THREAT OF DEATH, THE WOMEN HAD TO PUT 
EVERYTHING BACK IN EXACTLY THE PLACE THEY HAD FOUND 
IT IN THE ROOM. 
 
17. (U)  ON OCCASION THE WOMEN ALSO CLEANED THE 
OFFICES OF THE COMMANDERS.  THE WOMEN PRISONERS WERE 
ALWAYS HIDDEN FROM JOURNALISTS.  X. SAID SHE KNEW OF 
NO RAPES OR EXTREME BEATINGS OF THE WOMEN AT OMARSKA, 
ALTHOUGH THEY WERE TERRORIZED AND USED AS FORCED 
LABOR. 
 
-------------- 
MEN\'S QUARTERS 
-------------- 
 
18. (U)  OMARSKA HAD TWO BUILDINGS USED EXCLUSIVELY 
AS TORTURE CENTERS, THE \"WHITE HOUSE\" AND THE \"RED 
HOUSE.\"  ACCORDING TO X., F.B., AND A.V., AS WELL AS 
OTHER EX-DETAINEES, THE WHITE HOUSE WAS TERRIBLE, BUT 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
PAGE 04        ZAGREB  02038  06 OF 09  161651Z 
ON OCCASION PEOPLE RETURNED FROM IT.  NO ONE SENT TO 
THE RED HOUSE EVER CAME BACK.  THREE SPIRAL WATER 
TRANSPORTERS EXTENDED OUT OF THE RED HOUSE.  X. AND 
 
 
