SUBJECT:  CYGOOL:  HUMAN RIGHTS ABUSES IN BOSNIA- 
-         HERCEGOVINA - CASES OF X., F.B., AND A.V.; 
-         THE PERSONNEL STRUCTURE AT OMARSKA CAMP 
 
F.B. DESCRIBED THE WATER AS A STRANGE RUST RED COLOR. 
EDUCATED PRISONERS TENDED TO BE SENT TO THE RED 
HOUSE. (SEE SEPTEL - CASE OF S.H., OMARSKA SURVIVOR.) 
 
19. (U)  F.B. SAID HE WAS CONFINED ALONG WITH ABOUT 
470 OTHERS IN A ROOM WITH A SIMPLE CEMENT FLOOR ON 
THE SECOND-STORY OF A \"FACTORY\" BUILDING.  FROM A 
WINDOW IN THE ROOM, PRISONERS COULD SEE DIRECTLY INTO 
ONE ROOM OF THE \"WHITE HOUSE\" AND COULD SEE PRISONERS 
BEING TORTURED. 
 
20. (U)  F.B. SAID BEATINGS OFTEN WERE GIVEN NOT BY 
THE SHIFT GUARDS, BUT BY INDIVIDUALS FROM TOWN WHO 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  02038  07 OF 09  161659Z 
WERE ALLOWED INTO THE CAMP AFTER DARK TO GAIN REVENGE 
ON SPECIFIC PRISONERS (SEE PARA. 21 BELOW).  SANITARY 
FACILITIES WERE VIRTUALLY NON-EXISTENT.  EACH 
PRISONER WAS OCCASIONALLY ALLOWED TO USE A TOILET FOR 
TWO MINUTES OR LESS.  MOST PRISONERS WERE COVERED 
WITH LICE AND SUFFERED FROM DYSENTERY.  FOR LACK OF 
SPACE IN SOME ROOMS, PRISONERS HAD TO SLEEP IN A 
SITTING POSITION.  IN AT LEAST ONE SEVERELY CRAMPED 
ROOM, PRISONERS HAD TO TAKE TURNS SLEEPING; TWO- 
THIRDS OF THE PRISONERS WOULD STAND FOR AN HOUR WHILE 
ONE-THIRD SLEPT.  THESE SLEEPING SHIFT CHANGES WOULD 
CONTINUE THROUGHOUT THE NIGHT. 
 
--------------------------------------- 
SPECIFIC INCIDENTS OF EXTREME BRUTALITY 
--------------------------------------- 
 
21. (U)  F.B. SAID THAT A MUSLIM FRIEND NAMED MIR 
KARABASIC WAS TORTURED REGULARLY.  ONE DAY EMIR 
RETURNED TO THE SLEEPING ROOM WITH HIS BACK SEVERELY 
BURNED BY A GUARD.  THE PRISONERS HAD BEEN GIVEN SOME 
PORK LARD, AND F.B. RUBBED SOME OF THIS ON EMIR\'S 
CHARRED BACK.  TWO DAYS LATER, TWO SERBIAN BROTHERS 
WERE LET INTO THE CAMP AFTER FIVE O\'CLOCK.  THEY WERE 
DUSKO TADIC (NICKNAME DULE) AND LJUBO TADIC.  THEY 
OFTEN VISITED THE CAMP AT NIGHT. 
 
22. (U)  THE TADIC BROTHERS ENTERED THE SLEEPING 
QUARTERS CARRYING PISTOLS AND AUTOMATIC RIFLES.  THEY 
CALLED FOR EMIR, JASMIN HRMIC, AND (FNU) ALIC TO COME 
FORWARD.  THE THREE WERE BEATEN WITH RIFLE BUTTS AND 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
PAGE 04        ZAGREB  02038  07 OF 09  161659Z 
POLICE BATONS IN FULL VIEW OF THE OTHER PRISONERS, 
INCLUDING F.B.  THE TADIC BROTHERS FORCED ALIC FIRST 
TO DRINK A GLASS OF MOTOR OIL AND THEN TO DRINK THE 
 
 
