URINE OF THE OTHER TWO PRISONERS.  ALIC WAS NEXT 
BEATEN UNTIL HE WAS UNCONSCIOUS AND THEN AWAKENED 
WITH COLD WATER.  AFTER FURTHER BEATINGS, ALIC WAS 
FORCED TO TAKE HIS PANTS OFF.  THE TADIC BROTHERS 
THEN FORCED EMIR AND JASMIN TO BITE OFF ALIC\'S 
TESTICLES.  ALIC DIED OF HIS WOUNDS THAT NIGHT. 
ACCORDING TO F.B., THESE CRIMES WERE COMMITTED ON THE 
SHIFT OF MLADO RADIC. 
 
23. (LOU)  F.B. AND X. DESCRIBED THE BRUTAL DEATH OF 
ANOTHER PRISONER, SILVIJE SARIC (STRICTLY PROTECT), 
IDENTIFIED BELOW AS \"Y.\"   Y. WAS THE PRESIDENT OF 
THE HDZ IN PRIJEDOR AND A LAWYER FOR THE POST 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  02038  08 OF 09  161657Z 
OFFICE/TELEPHONE COMPANY (PTT). 
 
24. (U)  F.B.  REGULARLY SLEPT RIGHT NEXT TO Y.  Y. 
WAS TAKEN FOR QUESTIONING TO THE INSPECTORS ON THREE 
SEPARATE OCCASIONS, BUT REPORTEDLY GAVE THEM NO 
INFORMATION.  THIS QUESTIONING TOOK PLACE IN THE ROOM 
NEXT TO THE WOMEN\'S SLEEPING QUARTERS.  ON THE LAST 
OCCASION, X. HEARD HIM BEGGING AND SCREAMING ALL 
NIGHT.  SHE RECOGNIZED HIS VOICE THROUGH THE WALL. 
SHE HEARD HIM BEG THE GUARDS TO STOP BEATING HIM.  AT 
ONE POINT SHE HEARD HIM EXCLAIM, \"OH HOLY MOTHER, 
LOOK WHAT IS HAPPENING TO ME.\"  THERE WAS QUIET AND A 
VOICE FINALLY SAID, \"GET SOME WATER.\"  THEN HIS 
SCREAMS STARTED AGAIN.  Y. WAS BROUGHT BACK TO THE 
SLEEPING AREA, WHERE F.B. TRIED TO TAKE CARE OF HIM. 
F.B. SAID Y. LIVED IN A SEMI-CONSCIOUS STATE FOR TEN 
DAYS BUT THEN DIED.  F.B. BELIEVES THIS INCIDENT ALSO 
TOOK PLACE ON RADIC\'S SHIFT. 
 
25. (U)  F.B. TOLD OF AN INCIDENT INVOLVING A 
PRISONER WHO WAS A MUSLIM HODJA, OR HOLY MAN.  ONE 
DAY IN MAY CLOSE TO BAJREM, THE MUSLIM HOLY DAY, A 
GUARD NAMED (FNU) BAKAJ CALLED FOR \"THE HODJA\" TO GO 
WITH HIM.  THE GUARD WAS YOUNG, WITH TWO LARGE 
PLASTIC SURGERY MARKS ON HIS FACE.  THE HODJA 
RETURNED AFTER SEVERAL HOURS, LOOKING VIOLENTLY ILL. 
HE WAS FORCED TO WALK AROUND THE PRISONERS\' ROOM 
SAYING, \"I ATE PORK AND IT WAS DELICIOUS.\"  HE LAY 
NEAR F.B. AND TRIED TO KEEP FROM VOMITING AS HE SHOOK 
FROM CONVULSIONS.  HE TOLD F.B. HE HAD BEEN BEATEN 
AND FORCED AT GUNPOINT TO EAT HEAVY PORK MEAT (ON A 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
PAGE 04        ZAGREB  02038  08 OF 09  161657Z 
STOMACH THAT HAD BEEN EMPTY FOR WEEKS).  HE DID NOT 
WANT TO VOMIT FOR FEAR THE GUARDS WOULD FORCE HIM TO 
REPEAT THE EXERCISE. 
 
 
