NEAR FUTURE IN OTHER LOCALITIES IN NORTHERN BOSNIA. 
IN PARTICULAR, THEY FEAR AN EXODUS FROM COMMUNITIES 
NORTH OF TRAVNIK SUCH AS MAGLAJ AND ZAVIDOVICI. 
MEANWHILE, THEY COMMENTED THAT THE AUTHORITIES IN 
TUZLA, UNABLE TO COMMUNICATE WITH THE B-H GOVERNMENT 
