SUBJECT:  CGYOOL:  TUDJMAN SUMMONS DIP CORPS; SPELLS 
-         OUT POSITIONS ON B-H, UNPAS, OTHER ISSUES 
 
REF:  A) ZAGREB 2226 (NOTAL) 
 
