TAGS: PGOV, PREL, MOPS, PREF, HR, BK 
SUBJECT:  CGYOOL:  TUDJMAN SUMMONS DIP CORPS; SPELLS 
-         OUT POSITIONS ON B-H, UNPAS, OTHER ISSUES 
 
PERSONS STILL DISPLACED FROM THEIR HOMES -- ARE 
INCREASINGLY DISSATISFIED WITH AND FRUSTRATED BY 
DELAYS IN IMPLEMENTATION OF THE VANCE PLAN. 
 
11.  UNPROFOR HAS NOT SUCCEEDED EVEN IN IMPLEMENTING 
THE ESSENTIAL TASK OF DISARMING THE SERBS IN THE 
UNPAS, TUDJMAN STRESSED.  UNPROFOR HAS GOTTEN THE JNA 
OUT OF THE UNPAS AND, NOW, OUT OF PREVLAKA.  BUT 
PARAMILITARY AND IRREGULAR SERBIAN UNITS ARE GROWING 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  02290  04 OF 06  051645Z 
IN THE UNPAS AND NOW HAVE A STRENGTH OF AROUND 18,000 
ORGANIZED, WELL-ARMED MEN.  IN SECTOR EAST, FOR 
EXAMPLE, AROUND BELI MANASTIR, SERBIAN FORCES HAVE 16 
APC\'S \"PAINTED BLUE\" (PRESUMABLY \"MILITIA-BLUE\") PLUS 
10 T-34 TANKS, AND FIVE MORE TANKS IN BATINA.  IN 
SECTOR WEST, NOT ALL OF THE HEAVY WEAPONRY IS 30 KM 
FROM THE BORDER, AS REQUIRED; IN ONE LOCALE ALONE -- 
ON THE BORDER -- THE SERBS HAVE 7 TANKS AND 2 MORTAR 
BATTERIES.  IN SECTOR NORTH, AROUND GLINA AND VIRGIN 
MOST, THERE ARE SUBSTANTIAL NUMBERS OF SERB-HELD 
TANKS AND APC\'S.  AND IN OTHER AREAS, WHERE HEAVY 
ARMS HAVE SUPPOSEDLY BEEN ROUNDED UP, THEY ARE NOT 
WELL SECURED.  IN SECTOR SOUTH, THE SERBS HAVE 9 
TANKS, PLUS ARTILLERY AND MORTARS, AT GRACAC, AS WELL 
AS TANKS AT DRNIS.  IN KNIN, THERE IS A SERB- 
CONTROLLED COMPANY OF T-55 TANKS.  IN BARANJA (SECTOR 
EAST), THERE IS VIRTUALLY A NON-STOP FERRY OF ARMS 
AND PERSONNEL TO AND FROM SERBIA. 
 
12.  TUDJMAN ARGUED THAT THE SECURITY COUNCIL MUST 
AUTHORIZE UNPROFOR TO IMPLEMENT THEIR MANDATE, EVEN 
IF THAT REQUIRES RESORTING TO ARMS.  AMONG OTHER 
UNPROFOR SHORTCOMINGS, THERE HAD BEEN VIRTUALLY 
NOTHING DONE TO PERMIT THE RETURN OF THE DISPLACED. 
ON THE CONTRARY, EVEN UNDER THE EYES OF UNPROFOR NEW 
CRIMES ARE BEING COMMITTED BY SERBS.  IN SECTOR EAST, 
FOR EXAMPLE, THERE HAVE BEEN 600 (PRESUMABLY 
NON-SERBS) KILLED SINCE THE DEPLOYMENT OF UNPROFOR. 
IN BARANJA, NOT ONLY CROATS ARE PERSECUTED AND 
KILLED, BUT ALL NON-SERB NATIONALITIES, ESPECIALLY 
HUNGARIANS.  IN ADDITION, THE VANCE PLAN HAS NOT BEEN 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
PAGE 04        ZAGREB  02290  04 OF 06  051645Z 
IMPLEMENTED WITH REGARD TO REESTABLISHMENT OF ROAD 
AND RAIL LINKS AND OTHER COMMUNICATION.  THERE HAS 
BEEN LITTLE PROGRESS ON THE MASLENICA BRIDGE AND THE 
 
 
