TAGS: PGOV, PREL, MOPS, PREF, HR, BK 
SUBJECT:  CGYOOL:  TUDJMAN SUMMONS DIP CORPS; SPELLS 
-         OUT POSITIONS ON B-H, UNPAS, OTHER ISSUES 
 
PERUCA DAM, WHICH SUPPLIES MUCH OF DALMATIA\'S POWER 
-- AND ALL THIS BECAUSE OF THE INACTIVITY OF 
UNPROFOR, AND THEIR PERMITTING EXTREMIST ELEMENTS OF 
SERBS VIRTUALLY TO RUN FREE IN THE UNPAS. 
 
13.  CONTINUING, TUDJMAN SAID THAT UNPROFOR HAD ALSO 
NOT IMPLEMENTED ITS MANDATE TO CONTROL THE BORDERS 
BETWEEN CROATIA AND SERBIA AND BETWEEN CROATIA AND 
B-H.  HE ALLEGED EVIDENCE OF THE SERBS VIOLATING THE 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  02290  05 OF 06  051646Z 
SANCTIONS AGAINST IMPORT OF OIL AND OTHER GOODS INTO 
SERBIA/MONTENEGRO -- WITH THE ASSISTANCE OF UNPROFOR. 
 
14.  TUDJMAN SAID THE CROATIAN GOVERNMENT WOULD SEND 
A MEMORANDUM TO THE UN SECRETARY GENERAL.  HE ASKED 
THAT OTHER GOVERNMENTS SUPPORT CROATIA\'S STAND. 
CROATIA WANTS UNPROFOR IMMEDIATELY TO IMPLEMENT THE 
VANCE PLAN, TUDJMAN EMPHASIZED.  IN THAT REGARD, 
UNPROFOR CAN CONTINUE TO COUNT ON CROATIAN 
COOPERATION.  BUT, UNDER THESE CIRCUMSTANCES, CROATIA 
COULD NOT AGREE TO AN EXTENSION OF UNPROFOR\'S 
MANDATE, BECAUSE SERBIAN ELEMENTS ARE USING IT 
(UNPROFOR\'S PRESENCE) TO CONSOLIDATE THEIR POSITION 
IN THE UNPAS AND IN NEIGHBORING AREAS OF B-H. 
 
15.  TUDJMAN SAID CROATIA HAD PROVIDED THE POLITICAL 
PREREQUISITES FOR A RESOLUTION OF THE BASIC PROBLEM 
IN THE UNPAS (PRESUMABLY A REFERENCE TO THE LAW ON 
ABOLITION).  HE REFERRED TO SEVERAL INSTANCES IN 
WHICH GROUPS OF CROATIAN SERBS HAD VOLUNTARILY 
SURRENDERED ARMS \"FORCED ON THEM BY THE JNA\" IN 
HOPES OF NORMALIZING THEIR STATUS IN CROATIA. 
NONETHELESS, HE SAID, THE SITUATION IS WORSENING 
BECAUSE OF EXTREMIST ELEMENTS SUPPLIED BY BELGRADE. 
 
16.  HE SAID THAT CROATIA IS READY TO IMPLEMENT THE 
LAW ON LOCAL SELF-GOVERNMENT, INCLUDING IN THE 
SERBIAN AREAS, IN THE CONTEXT OF HOLDING ELECTIONS TO 
THE SECOND CHAMBER OF THE SABOR IN THE COMING 
TWO-THREE MONTHS.  IN THE MEANTIME, CROATIA WILL PASS 
A LAW AIMED AT CONTROLLING FURTHER ENCROACHMENTS ON 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
PAGE 04        ZAGREB  02290  05 OF 06  051646Z 
ITS TERRITORY; THIS WILL BE DONE AS A WARNING TO THE 
SERBS TO DESIST FROM FURTHER ACTIONS AND WAR CRIMES. 
 
 
 
