THEY WILL BE CARED FOR BY A FRIEND OR RELATIVE IN A 
THIRD COUNTRY IS ALLOWED TO TRANSIT CROATIA.  (NOTE: 
THE GERMAN EMBASSY SAYS IT PROCESSES AN AVERAGE OF 
1,000 SUCH CASES PER WEEK).  IN ADDITION, CROATIA 
RECENTLY ACCEPTED AN ESTIMATED 9,000 REFUGEES WHEN 
BOSANSKI BROD FELL TO SERBIAN FORCES.  IT HAS ALSO 
ACCEPTED SOME 10-20 PERCENT (LOW THOUSANDS) OF THE 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
