SUBJECT:  CGYOOL -- APPROACHING THE BREAKING POINT: 
-         CROATIA AND THE BOSNIAN REFUGEE PROBLEM 
 
WINTERIZED SHELTER OF ANY KIND LEFT IN CROATIA. 
70,000 B-H REFUGEES ARE STILL IN HOUSING INADEQUATE 
FOR THE COMING WINTER, ALTHOUGH GRANIC SAID THE 
CROATS HOPE SOON TO HAVE ALL THE REFUGEES MOVED INTO 
SOMETHING BETTER THAN TENTS.  (NOTE:  TODAY\'S PRESS, 
HOWEVER, CLAIMS IT WILL BE LATE DECEMBER BEFORE EVEN 
THE REFUGEES NOW HERE ARE ALL MOVED OUT OF TENTS.) 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  02392  07 OF 09  131617Z 
THE PROBLEM, HOWEVER, GOES BEYOND LIMITED PHYSICAL 
CAPACITY, GRANIC EMPHASIZED.  LOCAL AUTHORITIES ARE 
FLATLY REFUSING TO ACCEPT ADDITIONAL REFUGEES AND THE 
NEAR-CERTAIN HEIGHTENED SOCIAL TENSION THAT WOULD 
ACCOMPANY THEIR ARRIVAL. 
 
16.  GRANIC SAID THAT CROATIAN OFFICIALS HAVE FOUND 
IT VIRTUALLY IMPOSSIBLE TO LOCATE AN ACCEPTABLE SITE 
FOR A SECOND TRANSIT CENTER FOR EX-DETAINEES FROM 
B-H.  WITH SOME 1,500 UNHCR-CARED FOR EX-DETAINEES 
FREE TO ROAM IN DEPRESSED, WAR-TORN KARLOVAC, 
TENSIONS BETWEEN THEM AND THE TOWNSFOLK ARE RISING. 
AS A SOP TO THE KARLOVAC AUTHORITIES, THE GOC HAS HAD 
TO BUDGET ADDITIONAL PUBLIC WORKS FOR THE COMMUNITY. 
GRANIC HIMSELF WAS FINALLY ABLE IN RECENT DAYS TO 
LOCATE SPACE FOR 500-700 MORE EX-DETAINEES IN 
KARLOVAC (WHICH APPARENTLY WILL BE USED FOR SOME OF 
THE MANJACA EX-DETAINEES EXPECTED IMMINENTLY).  BUT 
KARLOVAC HAS FLATLY REFUSED TO TAKE ANY MORE 
EX-DETAINEES, AS HAVE DJAKOVAC AND VODICE, AMONG 
OTHER COMMUNITIES THAT HAVE BEEN APPROACHED.  GRANIC 
CONFIDED THAT HE NOW AVOIDS IF ALL POSSIBLE VISITING 
TOWNS WITH LARGE REFUGEES POPULATIONS, SO OFTEN HAS 
HE COME CLOSE TO BEING MOBBED BY IRATE CITIZENS.  HE 
COMMENTED THAT HE IS CALLED UPON EVERY DAY TO RESOLVE 
THREE OR FOUR LOCAL DISPUTES WHERE DISORDER IS 
THREATENED BETWEEN REFUGEES AND HOST COMMUNITIES. 
THE POTENTIAL SOCIAL PROBLEM IS COMPOUNDED BY THE 
FACT THAT REFUGEES IN CROATIA ARE NOT SUBJECT TO 
CONTROLS ON THEIR MOVEMENT.  (ANOTHER OF THE CROATS\' 
NIGHTMARE SCENARIOS IS A LARGE GROUP OF NEW REFUGEES 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
PAGE 04        ZAGREB  02392  07 OF 09  131617Z 
ON THE MOVE INSIDE CROATIA.) 
 
------------------------------------------ 
CROATIA REFUSES TO ABET \"ETHNIC CLEANSING\" 
------------------------------------------ 
 
 
