PRESENCE THERE OF THE CROATIAN ARMY AND SERBIAN 
MILITIAS, AND SOME TERRORISM. 
 
6.  SECTOR WEST IS GENERALLY QUIET; IMPLEMENTATION OF 
THE VANCE PLAN IS FURTHER ADVANCED THAN IN ANY OTHER 
SECTOR.  THE PROGRAMME OF VISITS OF DISPLACED PERSONS 
FROM BOTH SIDES TO THEIR FORMER VILLAGES IS 
PROGRESSING: AS OF LAST WEEK, 1,500 PEOPLE HAD 
VISITED 50 VILLAGES TO EXAMINE THE DAMAGES TO THEIR 
HOMES AND START PREPARATIONS FOR THEIR REPAIR.  THE 
AUSTRIAN GOVERNMENT HAS OFFERED 500 TEMPORARY HOUSING 
UNITS FOR PEOPLE WHO WISH TO WORK ON THEIR HOUSES 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  02400  02 OF 04  161003Z 
DURING THE WINTER.  IN ONE AREA NEIGHBORING SECTOR 
WEST, UNPROFOR HAS PROVIDED INFORMATION RELATING TO 
RESOLUTION 780 TO THE WAR CRIMES COMMISSION, WHICH 
WAS SCHEDULED TO MEET YESTERDAY FOR THE FIRST TIME. 
 
7.  IN SECTORS EAST AND SOUTH, THE TREND TOWARD 
ANARCHY CONTINUES.  GANGS OF TERRORISTS ROAM THE 
AREA, THERE ARE POLICE FORCES WHO DO NOT POLICE, 
PROSECUTORS WHO DO NOT PROSECUTE, AND COURTS THAT ARE 
AFRAID TO SIT.  (UNPROFOR MADE AVAILABLE A PAGE 
GIVING EXTRACTS FROM UNCIVPOL REPORTS SUMMARISING 
RECENT INCIDENTS FROM SECTORS EAST AND SOUTH).  MANY 
OF THESE ARE SMALL, NASTY, COWARDLY CRIMES, USUALLY 
ETHNICALLY BASED AND AIMED AT OLD PEOPLE LIVING 
ALONE.  THE MAJORITY ARE AGAINST CROATS LIVING IN 
SERB-CONTROLLED TERRITORIES, BUT THERE ARE ALSO SOME 
AGAINST SERBS LIVING IN CROAT-CONTROLLED AREAS.  IN A 
WAY, THERE HAS BEEN SOME IMPROVEMENT, AS THERE ARE 
FEWER MURDERS THAN BEFORE. 
 
8.  ALONG THE EDGES OF SECTOR SOUTH, SOME CEASE-FIRE 
VIOLATIONS, MAINLY BY THE CROATIAN ARMY, ARE PROBABLY 
PROVOCATIONS.  AS THERE HAS STILL NOT BEEN 
DISARMAMANT OF THE SERB MILITIA, THE CROATIAN ARMY 
HAS, IN SOME CASES, MOVED BACK UP FROM THE WITHDRAWAL 
LINE, TO THE CONFRONTATION LINE, AND THE RELATIVELY 
HEAVILY ARMED SERB MILITIA HAVE ALSO MOVED UP TO THAT 
LINE. 
 
--------------------------------------------- -- 
1,500 TONS OF EXPLOSIVES REPORTED IN PERUCA DAM 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
PAGE 04        ZAGREB  02400  02 OF 04  161003Z 
--------------------------------------------- -- 
 
9.  PERUCA DAM, (LOCATED) IN A PINK ZONE, HAS BEEN 
UNDER UNPROFOR CONTROL SINCE 14 SEPTEMBER.  THE WATER 
LEVEL IS NOW 357.62 METRES.  THE BRITISH ENGINEERING 
TEAM THAT SURVEYED THE DAM LAST WEEK WERE TOLD THAT 
 
 
