GENEVA FOR USDEL ICFY -- JACKOVICH; USVIENNA FOR USDEL CSCE 
 
E.O. 12356:  DECL: OADR 
TAGS:  PREL, PREF, PHUM, UN, HR 
SUBJECT:  CGYOOL:  UNPROFOR CHIEF SPEAKS OF ANARCHY IN 
-         UNPA\'S, LACK OF COOPERATION BY KRAJINA SERBS 
 
AND MILAN MARTIC, FOR A \"REMARKABLY FRANK\" 
DISCUSSION.  WITH REGARD TO RESOLUTION 769, WHICH 
REQUIRES UNPROFOR TO CONTROL THE CROSSING POINTS FROM 
THE UNITED NATIONS PROTECTED AREAS INTO OTHER PARTS 
OF THE FORMER YUGOSLAVIA, THE KNIN AUTHORITIES AGREED 
TO MOVE THEIR CHECKPOINTS BACK CA. 500 METRES FROM 
THE UNPROFOR CHECKPOINTS AT THE BOUNDARIES, EXCEPT ON 
FIVE BRIDGES; THESE ARE STILL UNDER NEGOTIATION. 
TALKS ON THE DISARMING OF THE SPECIAL MILITIA WERE 
NOT FRUITFUL AND DISCUSSIONS WILL CONTINUE. 
REGARDING RESOLUTION 762 ON THE PINK ZONES, WHICH 
CALLS FOR A STEP-BY-STEP RESTORATION OF CROATIAN 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  02400  04 OF 04  161005Z 
AUTHORITY IN THESE AREAS, IF THE LOCAL AUTHORITIES DO 
NOT ACCEPT THE BASIC ELEMENTS OF THE RESOLUTION, THE 
SECURITY COUNCIL WILL HAVE TO BE INFORMED.  UNPROFOR 
HAS NO INTENTION OF BEING AN ACCESSORY TO THE 
CONSOLIDATION OF THE RULE OF THE PINK ZONES BY 
AUTHORITIES OTHER THAN THOSE STATED IN THE RESOLUTION. 
 
14.  THE SERIOUS DESIRE FOR PEACE THAT IS APPARENT IN 
MANY PARTS OF THE REGION OF THE FORMER YUGOSLAVIA 
COULD BE ENDANGERED BY THE BLOCKAGES IN THE 
IMPLEMENTATION OF THE VANCE PLAN IN THE SECTORS. 
 
15.  AT PREVLAKA, APART FROM A FEW PROBLEMS, THE 
IMPLEMENTATION OF THE VANCE PLAN IS PROCEEDING QUITE 
WELL.  THE YUGOSLAV ARMY HAS WITHDRAWN, IN ACCORDANCE 
WITH THE VANCE PLAN, AND MILITARY OBSERVERS ARE NOW 
DEPLOYED.  THERE HAVE BEEN REPORTS, HOWEVER, OF 
CROATIAN ARMY ACTIVITIES IN ADJACENT AREAS. 
 
NEITZKE 
 
 
 
