14 SDS SERBS INDICTED IN DUBROVNIK FOR WAR CRIMES 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  02505  03 OF 03  251547Z 
--------------------------------------------- ---- 
 
9.  THE MILITARY DISTRICT COURT IN SPLIT OPENED 
LEGAL PROCEEDINGS AGAINST 14 MEMBERS OF THE 
SERBIAN DEMOCRATIC PARTY IN DUBROVNIK.  THEY ARE 
ACCUSED OF PARTICIPATING IN THE WAR AND HELPING 
THE YUGOSLAV ARMY AND SERBIAN EXTREMISTS.  FIVE OF 
THE ACCUSED ARE IN CUSTODY IN DUBROVNIK.  THE REST 
REMAIN AT LARGE. 
 
