THAT SOME 12 YUGOSLAV WARSHIPS HAD STOOD OFF 
DUBROVNIK AND BOMBARDED THE CITY.  ONE COULD 
UNDERSTAND, THE SENATOR SAID, SOME UNRULY ELEMENTS 
 
 
