TAGS: PREF, PHUM, HR, PHUM, HR, PHUM, HR, PHUM, HR, PHUM, HR, PHUM, HR, BK, War Crimes 
SUBJECT:  CYGOOL:  HUMAN RIGHTS ABUSES IN BOSNIA- 
-         HERCEGOVINA - CASE OF S.V., MUSLIM MALE, 42 
 
 
------------------------ 
INTRODUCTION AND SUMMARY 
------------------------ 
 
1.  (U)  THIS IS ONE IN A SERIES OF REPORTS ON 
SPECIFIC AND GROSS HUMAN RIGHTS ABUSES IN BOSNIA AND 
HERCEGOVINA (B-H) BASED ON PERSONAL INTERVIEWS WITH 
THE SUBJECTS NAMED.  THE SUBJECT IN THIS REPORT 
AGREED TO SPEAK ONLY AFTER RECEIVING ASSURANCES THAT 
HIS NAME WOULD NOT/NOT BE USED PUBLICLY FOR FEAR THAT 
THAT WOULD ENDANGER RELATIVES STILL UNDER SERBIAN 
DETENTION IN B-H. 
 
2.  (LOU)  SERIF VELIC (PROTECT) IS A 42-YEAR-OLD 
MUSLIM METALWORKER FROM KEVLJANI.  HE WAS INTERNED LN 
THE SERBIAN-RUN OMARSKA CAMP FROM MAY 27 UNTIL AUGUST 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  02544  01 OF 06  011240Z 
28 WHEN HE WAS TAKEN TO MANJACA CAMP.  HE WAS HELD 
THERE UNTIL HIS RELEASE ON NOV. 14 TO THE KARLOVAC 
TRANSIT CENTER FOR EX-DETAINEES.  VELIC WAS ABLE TO 
DESCRIBE IN GRAPHIC DETAIL THE SEVERE BEATINGS HE 
RECEIVED IN OMARSKA.  HE WAS INTERVIEWED IN KARLOVAC 
ON NOV. 23 AND 25 AND WAS JUDGED CREDIBLE.  VELIC IS 
IDENTIFIED BELOW AS \"S.V.\"  END INTRODUCTION AND 
SUMMARY. 
 
------------------- 
DETAILS OF THE CASE 
------------------- 
 
3.  (U)  S.V. IS A 42-YEAR-OLD BOSNIAN MUSLIM 
METALWORKER FROM A MUSLIM VILLAGE OF KEVLJANI, NEAR 
PRIJEDOR.  HE WAS INTERNED IN THE SERBIAN-RUN OMARSKA 
CAMP FOR THREE MONTHS AND IN MANJACA CAMP FOR THREE 
MONTHS.  S.V. WAS THE HEAD OF THE TERITORIJALNE 
- 
ODBRANA (TO) IN KEVLJANI BEFORE THE WAR.  THE 
TERRITORIAL DEFENSE GROUP WAS COMPOSED OF MUSLIMS, 
CROATS, AND SERBS.  THE GROUP HAD 7 AUTOMATIC RIFLES, 
4 M48 RIFLES, AND 2 PISTOLS.  THE TO IN KEVLJANI 
COMBINED WITH THE VILLAGES OF HADZICI, JAKUPOVICI, 
AND GORNJI PETROV GAJ.  THE GROUP HAD 23 GUNS TOTAL, 
SAID S.V. 
 
4.  (U)  ON MAY 26, SERBS ATTACKED HIS VILLAGE.  THE 
VILLAGERS FLED TO THE WOODS, BUT AFTER SPENDING THE 
NIGHT IN THE WOODS UNDER HEAVY SHELLING, MANY WOMEN 
WANTED TO SURRENDER.  S.V. AND AN IMAM LED A GROUP OF 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
PAGE 04        ZAGREB  02544  01 OF 06  011240Z 
WOMEN AND CHILDREN UNDER A WHITE FLAG TO THE SCHOOL 
 
 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
