STOOD SPREAD-EAGLE AGAINST THE WALL WITH THE FIRST 
THREE FINGERS HELD UP OF EACH HAND.  (NOTE:  THIS IS 
THE SERBIAN CHETNIK SYMBOL.  END NOTE.)  HE WAS 
BEATEN WITH BATONS ON ALL HIS JOINTS, AND HIS LEGS 
