SUBJECT:  CGY001:  THE UGLY VIRUS OF MORAL SYMMETRY - 
-         WHO IS DOING THE \"ETHNIC CLEANSING\" IN B-H? 
 
ARGUE THAT CERTAIN CROATIAN ELEMENTS, NOTABLY HOS, 
DID NOT ENGAGE IN ISOLATED CRIMES AS HEINOUS AS SOME 
OF THOSE ROUTINELY COMMITTED BY BOSNIAN SERB FORCES. 
BUT WE HAVE NO EVIDENCE OF CROATIAN FORCES ENGAGING 
IN ETHNIC CLEANSING AS THAT TERM IS NOW USEFULLY 
APPLIED TO THE CONCLUSIVELY-DOCUMENTED BOSNIAN SERB 
PRACTICE OF:  BOMBARDING A VILLAGE FROM AFAR, ENTERING 
IT IN A SHOWY DISPLAY OF MILITARY FORCE, IMMEDIATELY 
COMMITTING SUCH TERRORIZING PUBLIC ATROCITIES AS 
SLITTING A DOZEN OR SO PERSONS\' THROATS ON THEIR 
DOORSTEP AND RAPING A YOUNG GIRL OR TWO IN FRONT OF 
THEIR FAMILIES AND OTHER TOWNSFOLK IN THE PUBLIC 
SQUARE, THEN TRANSPORTING THE MEN AND BOYS TO TORTURE 
AND DEATH CAMPS AND THE WOMEN AND GIRLS TO SERBIAN 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  02586  02 OF 03  041602Z 
MILITARY BROTHELS.  ANYONE WHO HAS READ THE ACCOUNTS 
OF THE SERBIAN DEATH CAMP SURVIVORS WILL KNOW THAT 
THIS IS NOT HYPERBOLE. 
- 
5.  CULPABILITY FOR THE EVENTS IN NOVI TRAVNIK AND 
PROZOR IN MID-OCTOBER IS DISPUTED.  THE CROATS CLAIM 
TO HAVE RADIO INTERCEPT \"PROOF\" OF ORDERS GIVEN BY 
RADICAL MUSLIM ELEMENTS TO KILL CROATS.  THERE ARE 
OTHER REPORTS OF BATTLE CRIES FROM CROATIAN ELEMENTS 
TO KILL MUSLIMS.  AND THE AFTERMATH INDICATES THAT 
MUSLIM CIVILIANS DID SUFFER DISPROPORTIONATELY. 
NOTWITHSTANDING WHO IS MORE GUILTY FOR THIS BOUT OF 
CROATIAN/MUSLIM MADNESS, BOTH SIDES ARE PAINFULLY 
AWARE THAT IT CONTRIBUTED DIRECTLY TO THE FALL OF 
JAJCE.  IN THE WAKE OF THAT TRAGEDY, IZETBEGOVIC AND 
TUDJMAN SAY THEY HAVE CLEARED THE AIR, AND CROATIAN 
AND MUSLIM FORCES APPEAR TO HAVE REESTABLISHED A 
MODICUM OF CIVILITY AND COOPERATION IN MILITARY 
ACTIONS.  ALTHOUGH WE ARE NOT AWARE OF SUBSEQUENT 
\"PROZORS,\" NONE OF THIS IS TO SAY THAT THERE WON\'T BE 
OTHER CROATIAN/MUSLIM SKIRMISHES FROM WHICH MUSLIMS 
AND/OR CROATS MAY FLEE.  IT IS TO SAY, HOWEVER, THAT 
BY NO REASONABLE STRETCH OF MIND OR LANGUAGE DOES 
\"PROZOR\" CONSTITUTE EVIDENCE OF CROATIAN ETHNIC 
CLEANSING, LET ALONE A LIKELIHOOD OF \"CONTINUED\" 
CROATIAN ETHNIC CLEANSING. 
 
6.  THE PERVERSE IRONY IN THIS TIRESOME CHARGE IS 
EVIDENT IN WHAT UNHCR SPECIAL ENVOY MENDILUCE TOLD 
EUR/EE DIRECTOR HABIB NOV 20.  MENDILUCE OBSERVED 
THAT SOME 350,000 MUSLIMS ARE NOW LIVING OR SHELTERING 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
PAGE 04        ZAGREB  02586  02 OF 03  041602Z 
IN CROATIAN-DEFENDED B-H (IN ADDITION TO THE OVER 
350,000 B-H MUSLIM REFUGEES IN CROATIA).  MENDILUCE 
NOTED THAT ONE OF THE KEY PROBLEMS WITH THE BOSNIAN 
CROATS WAS THEIR APPARENT DETERMINATION TO KEEP OUT 
 
 
