PARLIAMENT PASSES ECON CONCESSIONS LAW 
-------------------------------------- 
 
5.  THE CROATIAN SABOR PASSED A LAW ON DECEMBER 23 
REGULATING CONCESSIONS FOR NATURAL RESOURCE 
DEVELOPMENT AND OTHER SPECIALIZED PROJECTS.  AMONG 
ITS PROVISIONS IS THE RIGHT FOR BOTH CROATIAN AND 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  02816  02 OF 02  241220Z 
FOREIGN COMPANIES TO HOLD A CONCESSION FOR UP TO 
99 YEARS.  THE LAW ALSO GIVES PARLIAMENT THE RIGHT 
TO CLEAR ON GOVERNMENT GRANTED CONCESSIONS AND 
GIVES LOCAL GOVERNMENTS A ROLE IN DETERMINING THE 
PRICE TO BE PAID FOR A CONCESSION IN THEIR 
RESPECTIVE AREAS. 
 
