FIGHTING THIS WEEKEND WAS ZEPA, EAST OF SARAJEVO. 
ON DECEMBER 27 TWO GROUND-TO-GROUND ROCKETS 
REPORTEDLY STRUCK ZEPA, KILLING THREE AND WOUNDING 
NINE OTHERS.  THE REPORT NOTED THAT ZEPA IS 
WITHOUT FOOD, AND CHILDREN AND OLD PEOPLE ARE 
 
 
