INDEPENDENCE IS WHAT \"PRECIPITATED A CIVIL WAR.\"  WE 
SUGGEST SUBSTITUTING THE ACCURATE LANGUAGE OF 92 
BELGRADE 3998 //BLOCKED BY SERBIA IN ITS ATTEMPT TO 
RESTRUCTURE YUGOSLAVIA AS A LOOSE FEDERATION, THE 
REPUBLIC OF CROATIA DECLARED ITS INDEPENDENCE ON JUNE 
25, 1991, AND SOUGHT INTERNATIONAL RECOGNITION.// 
AND THEN IMMEDIATELY ADD //THAT ACTION WAS SEIZED 
UPON BY THE AUTHORITIES IN BELGRADE TO UNLEASH THE 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
PAGE 02        ZAGREB  02863  02 OF 08  311858Z 
OVERWHELMINGLY SERBIAN-LED YUGOSLAV NATIONAL ARMY 
(JNA) AGAINST CROATIAN TOWNS AND CITIES IN ORDER TO 
DESTROY THE FLEDGLING CROATIAN STATE OR LEAVE IT 
CRIPPLED INDEFINITELY.  THEY ESTABLISHED CONTROL OVER 
A NUMBER OF AREAS WHERE CROATS OF SERBIAN NATIONALITY 
WERE PREDOMINANT AS WELL AS OVER AREAS WHERE SERBS 
HAD BEEN IN A MINORITY.  THE JNA WAS ASSISTED IN THIS 
EFFORT BY PARAMILITARY FORCES WHO INVADED FROM SERBIA 
AND FROM MONTENEGRO AND BY LOCAL SERBIAN IRREGULARS. 
THESE UNITS WERE OFTEN ORGANIZED AND LED BY REGULAR 
JNA OFFICERS OR THEIR SURROGATES AND ALL WERE 
DIRECTLY SUPPLIED WITH WEAPONS AND AMMUNITION BY THE 
JNA.// 
 
10.  REF A, NOTE ONE: CROATIA DID NOT ISSUE A FORMAL 
DECLARATION OF WAR.  RESTRICTIONS/EMERGENCY POWERS 
INCLUDED LARGELY CURFEWS, BLACKOUTS, AND SIMILAR 
CIVIL DEFENSE MEASURES.  MOST OF THESE, INSTITUTED 
INFORMALLY OR AT LOCAL LEVELS, HAVE LONG SINCE CEASED 
IN AREAS NOT STILL UNDER BOMBARDMENT FROM SERBIAN 
FORCES IN BOSNIA.  FOR EXAMPLE, THE CURFEW IN 
DUBROVNIK WAS LIFTED BEFORE CHRISTMAS AND WILL NOT BE 
REINSTATED. 
 
11.  PARA 6, SENTENCE TWO: THIS IS INACCURATE.  THE 
AREAS OVER WHICH CROATIAN AUTHORITY IS TO BE 
REESTABLISHED UNDER THE VANCE PLAN WERE NOT AND STILL 
ARE NOT SOLELY \"SERB-INHABITED.\"  SECTOR WEST IS NOT 
EVEN LARGELY SERBIAN-CONTROLLED.  NOR ARE SERBS THE 
ONLY MINORITY IN THE UNPAS.  WE SUGGEST SUBSTITUTING 
//THE VANCE PLAN WAS TO PROVIDE FOR NORMALIZING THE 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  02863  02 OF 08  311858Z 
OCCUPIED AREAS THROUGH DEMILITARIZATION, THE RETURN 
OF DISPLACED PERSONS, AND THE REESTABLISHMENT OF 
CROATIAN GOVERNMENT AUTHORITY, WITH ASSURANCES FOR 
MINORITY POPULATIONS.// 
 
12.  REF A, NOTE TWO: WITHDRAWAL OF JNA UNITS WAS 
SUPPOSEDLY COMPLETED IN THE SPRING AND SUMMER. 
HOWEVER, MANY OF THESE SOLDIERS IN JNA UNITS STAYED 
ON I SERBIAN-OCCUPIED PARTS OF CROATIA (WHAT BECAME 
THE UNPAS) AND \"CONVERTED\" TO THE SO-CALLED \"POLICE 
FORCE\" OR \"SPECIAL POLICE.\"  IN ADDITION, JNA UNITS 
CONTINUED TO OCCUPY THE PREVLAKA PENINSULA AND REGION 
AROUND DUBROVNIK LONG AFTER THEY HAD AGREED WITH UN 
NEGOTIATORS TO DEPART.  THE LAST JNA UNITS LEFT ONLY 
IN THE FIRST WEEK OF NOVEMBER. 
 
13.  PARA 6, LAST SENTENCE: THIS IS THE FIRST 
REFERENCE OF MANY IN REF A TO THE \"RSK,\" AN ENTITY 
WHICH NO COUNTRY RECOGNIZES.  IT IS NOT AN 
APPELLATION USED BY ANYONE IN CROATIA OUTSIDE OF THE 
UNPAS, INCLUDING CROATIAN SERBS.  IT HAS NO LEGAL 
STANDING AND NO GOVERNMENTAL STRUCTURES WORTHY OF THE 
NAME.  ITS SO-CALLED OFFICIALS ARE IN MANY CASES 
PERSONALLY PERSECUTING NOT ONLY CROATS AND HUNGARIANS 
AND OTHER MINORITIES BUT ALSO MODERATE SERBS AS 
WELL.  THROUGHOUT THIS REPORT, \"RSK\" SHOULD BE 
REPLACED WITH, AS APPROPRIATE, \"THE UNITED NATIONS 
PROTECTED AREAS,\" \"THE UNPAS,\" OR, WHERE NECESSARY, 
\"THE UNPA SERBS.\" 
 
14.  REF A, NOTE 3: THIS OFFICE OPERATES ALMOST 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
PAGE 04        ZAGREB  02863  02 OF 08  311858Z 
COMPLETELY SECRETLY.  THERE HAVE BEEN ALLEGATIONS, 
WHICH WE CANNOT SUBSTANTIATE, THAT PERSONS UNDER THIS 
OFFICE, HAVE BEEN IMPLICATED IN HUMAN RIGHTS ABUSES 
AGAINST CROATIANS OF SERBIAN NATIONALITY.  READERS 
INFORMED ABOUT CROATIA WILL DRAW THE CORRECT 
 
 
