COLLABORATORS.  THE IN ABSENTIA INDICTMENTS INVOLVE 
MOSTLY SERBS WHO ASSISTED THE JNA IN LAST YEAR\'S 
ATTACKS AND/OR WHO WERE ACTIVE IN SERBIAN 
PARAMILITARY GANGS. 
 
