//FORCED RESETTLEMENT//.  THE TERM ETHNIC CLEANSING 
SHOULD BE RESERVED FOR THE SPECIFIC PATTERN OF 
TERRORIST CLEARING ACTIONS OF BOSNIAN SERBS. 
 
