14.  \"A FRANKENSTEIN WAS CREATED HERE,\" LANG OBSERVED 
IN CONCLUSION.  ALL MEMBERS OF THE GROUP AGREED THAT 
FAILURE TO DEAL FIRMLY WITH THOSE RESPONSIBLE FOR 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  00176  04 OF 04  131754Z 
MASSIVE ETHNIC WARFARE AND ITS ATTENDENT ATROCITIES 
WILL SEND THE WRONG SIGNALS ABOUT INTERNATIONAL RESOLVE 
FOR OTHER CONFLICTS THAT ARE EVEN NOW BOILING OVER. 
 
15.  A/S SHATTUCK RE-EMPHASIZED THE IMPORTANCE OF 
BRINGING TO JUSTICE THOSE WHO ARE RESPONSIBLE FOR WAR 
CRIMES, BUT HE ALSO STRESSED THE IMPORTANCE OF DUE 
PROCESS AND LEGAL RIGOR IN MAKING THE CASES.  IF 
INDIVIDUALS RESPONSIBLE FOR CRIMES AGAINST HUMANITY CAN 
BE BROUGHT TO LEGAL ACCOUNT IN A CIVILIZED PROCESS, 
\"THEN THEY HAVE NOT WON,\" SHATTUCK SAID. 
 
