BOSNIAN CROATS AS \"USTASHA.\"  OFFICIAL B-H GOVERNMENT 
ANNOUNCEMENTS HAVE ALSO BEGUN USING THE TERM.  THE 
DAILY \"REVIEW OF MAJOR EVENTS\" PREPARED BY THE B-H 
FOREIGN MINISTRY AND DISTRIBUTED BY THE BOSNIAN EMBASSY 
IN ZAGREB NOW REFERS TO CROAT FORCES AS USTASHA. 
 
