SUBJECT: TFSROL:  SEVERE HUMAN RIGHTS ABUSES IN B-H: 
         EYE-WITNESS DESCRIBES TORTURE/EXECUTIONS IN 
         LUKA AND BATKOVIC CAMPS, NAMES PERPETRATORS 
 
5.  (LOU)  AFTER ABOUT 15 MINUTES, THE GUARDS CALLED 
THE WITNESS\'S NAME FOR A \"HEARING.\"  A FEW MINUTES 
EARLIER,  A RELATIVE OF THE WITNESS, AKIB HADZAJLIC 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  00827  02 OF 04  281646Z 
(STRICTLY PROTECT), HEREAFTER REFERRED TO AS A.H., 
HAD BEEN CALLED.  UPON ENTERING THE \"HEARING ROOM,\" 
THE WITNESS SAW A.H. LYING ON THE FLOOR IN A POOL OF 
BLOOD HOLDING A CLOTH PRESSED AGAINST HIS HEAD.  THE 
WITNESS WAS IMMEDIATELY HIT FROM BEHIND BY A MAN WITH 
A RUBBER TRUNCHEON, CAUSING HIM TO FALL ON TOP OF 
A.H.  THE WITNESS WAS THEN ASKED IF HE KNEW WHERE 
A.H. HAD HIDDEN A VIDEO CAMERA WITH WHICH HE 
ALLEGEDLY WAS FILMING EVENTS IN BRCKO FOR CROATIAN 
TELEVISION.  WHEN THE WITNESS SAID THAT A.H. NEVER 
HAD SUCH A CAMERA, THE WITNESS WAS KICKED AND BEATEN 
BY THE SERB INTERROGATORS, ALL OF WHOM WERE F 
ROM 
BIJELJINA.  BOTH MEN WERE THEN ASKED WHERE THEY HAD 
HIDDEN ARMS, AND WHEN THEY SAID THEY HAD NEVER HAD 
ANY WEAPONS, THEY WERE KICKED AND BEATEN UNTIL THE 
WITNESS WAS BLEEDING FROM HIS EARS. 
 
6.  (U) THE WITNESS WAS THEN ORDERED TO MAKE THE 
ORTHODOX CATHOLIC SIGN OF THE CROSS.  THE WITNESS 
ASKED TO BE SHOWN THE PROPER WAY TO DO THIS, AND THEN 
PROCEEDED TO GENUFLECT 20 TO 30 TIMES BEFORE MAKING A 
MISTAKE FOR WHICH THE WITNESS WAS AGAIN KICKED AND 
BEATEN, LOSING A TOOTH.  THE WITNESS WAS THEN LED OUT 
OF THE ROOM AS THREE MORE PRISONERS WERE BROUGHT IN. 
THESE WERE ADAM ZELEZIC AND HIS SON MLADEN, AND AN 
ELDERLY MAN, HAZIM KARAHASANOVIC, WHO WAS BORN IN 
1908.  OUTSIDE THE HEARING ROOM, THE WITNESS WAS TOLD 
TO WAIT NEXT TO A.H., WHO WAS COMPLETELY COVERED IN 
BLOOD.  BELIEVING THEY WOULD BE KILLED, THE WITNESS 
RAN BACK TO THE WAREHOUSE.  A.H., WHO WAS UNABLE TO 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
PAGE 04        ZAGREB  00827  02 OF 04  281646Z 
WALK, WAS, INDEED, KILLED.  AFTER 20 MINUTES, THE 
THREE OTHER PRISONERS RETURNED TO THE WAREHOUSE. 
ADAM AND MLADEN WERE INJURED BUT ABLE TO WALK.  THE 
OLD MAN, HAZIM, HAD TO BE CARRIED IN. 
 
7.  (U) SOME TIME LATER A POLICEMAN FROM BIJELJINA 
CAME TO THE WAREHOUSE AND ORDERED THE PRISONERS TO 
PAIR OFF IN THE MIDDLE OF THE ROOM AND TO PUNCH EACH 
OTHER IN THE FACE.  AFTERWARD, TWO OTHER POLICEMEN 
ENTERED. THEY STOOD BEHIND THE PRISONERS AND BEAT 
ANYONE WHO DID NOT STRIKE HIS PARTNER HARD ENOUGH. 
THE WITNESS SAID HE WAS SEVERELY BEATEN BY HIS 
PARTNER, WHO WAS MUCH YOUNGER AND VERY STRONG.  THIS 
LASTED ABOUT TWO HOURS, UNTIL ALL THE PAIRS WERE 
FINISHED.  THEY WERE THEN FORCED TO HAVE BOXING 
MATCHES.  DURING THIS PHASE, THE WITNESS\' FATHER, WHO 
WAS 70 YEARS OLD, WAS FORCED TO BOX A MAN OF 20.  FOR 
THE REST OF THE EVENING SERBS WOULD ENTER THE 
 
 
