12. (U) THE WITNESS SAID A PIT WAS DUG ABOUT 200 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  00872  04 OF 05  021701Z 
METERS FROM THE FARM ALONG A BROOK.  HE SAID THE 
DIMENSIONS WERE THREE TO FOUR METERS WIDE BY 30 
METERS LONG BY TWO METERS DEEP.  CORPSES OF MEN, 
WOMEN, AND CHILDREN WERE BROUGHT TO THE PIT AND 
THEN COVERED WITH A WHITE SUBSTANCE FROM 20 KILO 
DRUMS.  HE THOUGHT IT WAS SOME KIND OF 
PESTICIDE.  IT HAD A STRONG ODOR OF CHLORINE. 
AFTER UNLOADING, THE TRUCK DRIVERS WOULD CLEAN 
OUT THE TRUCKS AT A FIRE HYDRANT AT THE FARM. 
WHEN THE PIT WAS FULL, THE SERBS BROUGHT A FRONT 
END LOADER AND COVERED IT WITH DIRT.  THEN, HE 
SAID, THEY BROUGHT MATERIAL FROM THE RUINS OF 
THE BRCKO MOSQUE TO COVER THE DIRT.  FINALLY, 
THEY ADDED ANOTHER LAYER OF DIRT FROM A NEARBY 
HILL, ROLLED THE GRAVE FLAT, AND PLANTED GRASS. 
 
13. (U) THE WITNESS SAID THAT, TO REACH THE 
LIMITED OFFICIAL USE                                     6 
 
GRAVE SITE, ONE SHOULD DRIVE EAST FROM BRCKO. 
AFTER ABOUT ONE AND ONE-HALF KILOMETERS (HALFWAY 
TO THE ENTRANCE OF THE FARM) THERE IS A BRIDGE 
ACROSS A BROOK.  DO NOT CROSS THE BRIDGE, BUT 
EXIT THE VEHICLE ON THE RIGHT SIDE, AND THEN 
WALK ALONG THE EDGE OF THE BROOK AWAY FROM THE 
ROAD FOR ABOUT 70 METERS.  HE BELIEVED THERE ARE 
200 OR MORE BODIES AT THIS LOCATION. 
 
14. (U) THE WITNESS HEARD FROM THE TRUCK DRIVERS 
WHO BROUGHT THE BODIES TO THE MASS GRAVE 
DESCRIB 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
PAGE 04        ZAGREB  00872  04 OF 05  021701Z 
ED ABOVE THAT, BEFORE THEY STARTED USING 
THE PIT, THEY HAD TRANSPORTED BODIES TO A PLACE 
WHERE THE BONES OF ANIMALS WERE INCINERATED TO 
PRODUCE CATTLE FEED.  THEY USED THIS INCINERATOR 
AS LONG AS COAL WAS AVAILABLE.  ABOUT 100 METERS 
BEHIND THIS LOCATION WAS THE BRCKO TOWN GARBAGE 
DEPOT AND A CANAL DOWN TO THE SAVA RIVER.  THE 
WITNESS SAID IT WAS RUMORED THAT THERE MIGHT BE 
ANOTHER MASS GRAVE UNDER THE GARBAGE, BUT HE HAD 
NO DIRECT KNOWLEDGE OF THIS. 
 
