KORENIC, ADAN AHMEDOVIC, AND MELI HAMIDOVIC.  THEY 
ALL WERE PUT IN A CAR AND TAKEN TO AN APARTMENT IN 
THE \"S\" SETTLEMENT (A NEIGHBORHOOD IN 
BRCKO).  IN THE APARTMENT WERE FIVE OR SIX BRCKO 
