THEY WERE REGULARLY VISITED BY ONE MISO DORBERMAN WHO 
WOULD BEAT AND MISTREAT THEM.  ON JUNE 18, TWO BUSES 
ARRIVED AT HIS BUILDING, AND ALL THE ABLE-BODIED MEN 
(INCLUDING THE WITNESS) WERE PUT IN ONE WHILE THE 
WOMEN, CHILDREN, AND ELDERLY BOARDED THE OTHER.  THE 
MEN\'S BUS WENT TO LUKA.  THE WITNESS DID NOT KNOW 
WHERE THE OTHER BUS WENT. 
 
