ACCENTS WOULD COME IN FROM SERBIA TO ABUSE THEM.  ALL 
DURING THE WEEK, THEY WOULD BE BEATEN AND HUMILIATED 
BY LOCAL \"CETNIKS.\"  THESE INCLUDED:  RANKO CESIC; 
