ROOMS.\"  HE SAID THE BED WAS SOAKED WITH BLOOD. 
WITNESS DARED NOT BE SEEN TALKING TO THESE GIRLS, SO 
HE DID NOT TRY TO SPEAK WITH THEM.  THE MAIN BOSSES 
OF THESE GIRLS WERE THE PREVIOUSLY-MENTIONED SEKA, 
HER DAUGHTER VIOLETA, AND LIDIJA JEVTIC FROM BRCKO. 
- 
