IDENTIFICATION OF PROTECTED THIRD PARTIES 
----------------------------------------- 
 
24. (LOU)  THIRD PARTIES MENTIONED BY THE WITNESS WHO 
MERIT PROTECTION OR PRIVACY ARE IDENTIFIED AS 
FOLLOWS: 
THE SERBS WHO SAVED THE WITNESS\'S LIFE (REF 
PARA 8) WERE NINO SIMEUNOVIC, A FORMER POLICE 
INSPECTOR; DRAGISA (LNU); ZVJEZDAN MILICEVIC, AKA 
ADOLF (HE WAS THE ONE WHO SELECTED WHICH INDIVIDUALS 
TO TAKE); RATKO ZARIC, AND PERO ZARIC.  ALSO IN PARA 
8 ABOVE, THE TWO POLICEMEN INVOLVED WERE DOBRICA 
MILOSEVIC AND DRAGAN ZIVKOVIC, AND THE TWO OTHER 
SERBS WHO SAVED OTHER PRISONERS WERE SLOBODAN 
LJUBICIC AND LJUBICA POZNANOVIC.  IN PARA 19, THE 
MUSLIM GIRLS THE WITNESS COULD IDENTIFY WERE LEJLA 
SULEJMANOVIC, FAHIRA CACKOVIC, SABINA DELALIC, AND 
SELJA (LNU). 
 
