SIPDIS 
 
 
E.O. 12356:  N/A 
TAGS:  PHUM, MOPS, PINS, PREL, PREF, BK, HR 
SUBJECT:  THE NEST OF EVIL:  SERBS INTENSIFY ATROCITIES IN 
          BANJA LUKA 
 
     F)  NON-SERBS WERE ROUTINELY INTIMIDATED INTO 
COMPLETING DOCUMENTS REQUESTING THAT THE GOVERNMENT ASSUME 
OWNERSHIP OF THEIR PROPERTIES.  THESE DOCUMENTS, USUALLY 
ISSUED ONLY AFTER PAYING SUBSTANTIAL FEES, APPEARED TO 
HAVE BEEN REQUIRED FOR \"PERMISSION\" TO LEAVE BANJA LUKA. 
 
     G)  T 
HE SERBIAN HOSPITAL ADMINISTRATOR ANNOUNCED VIA 
TELEVISION, RADIO, AND PUBLICATIONS THAT NO MUSLIM OR 
CROATIAN BABIES WOULD BE BORN IN THE HOSPITAL WHILE HE WAS 
IN CHARGE. 
 
     H)  ONE WOMAN HAD BEEN BEATEN NINE TIMES DURING THE 
PAST TWO YEARS BY MASKED SERBS TRYING TO FORCE HER TO 
RELINQUISH HER APARTMENT.  SHE HAD LOST TEETH, AND HAD 
SCARS UNDER ONE EYE AND ON HER UPPER LIP FROM THESE 
VICIOUS ASSAULTS.  THESE BEATINGS ALSO OCCURRED FOLLOWING 
THE DISCOVERY THAT SHE HAD HELPED ONE SON TO FLEE TO 
SWEDEN.  HER ASSAILANTS WERE, THEY SAID, INCENSED THAT 
THEY HAD BEEN DENIED AN OPPORTUNITY TO TORTURE OR KILL HIM 
FIRST. 
 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  01217  02 OF 02  251809Z 
     I)  TWO MEN, ONE OF WHOM HAD A SERB SON-IN-LAW, WERE 
TAKEN AWAY BY A SQUAD OF SERBIAN SOLDIERS.  THE NEXT DAY 
THEIR BODIES WERE FOUND NEAR BANJA LUKA.  ONE WAS SHOT, 
THE OTHER CHARRED. 
 
---- 
NOTE 
---- 
 
5.  THESE ACCOUNTS CONSTITUTE ONLY A HANDFUL OF THE MANY 
ATROCITIES REPORTEDLY WITNESSED BY RECENT ARRIVALS FROM 
BANJA LUKA.  INDIVIDUAL ACCOUNTS WILL BE REPORTED IN 
SEPTELS. 
 
GALBRAITH 
 
 
