UPCOMING DART TRAVEL IN B-H 
--------------------------- 
 
2.  DART TEAM MEMBER T. KNIGHT IS SCHEDULED TO 
TRAVEL WITH CONGRESSIONAL STAFFER, M. BARATTA, TO 
SARAJEVO FROM APRIL 7 - 9.  IN ADDITION, FROM 
APRIL 10 TO APRIL 15, DART FIELD OFFICER B. 
STEUBNER IS SCHEDULED TO TRAVEL TO TUZLA WITH THE 
U.S. INTERAGENCY GROUP INVESTING WAR CRIMES IN 
THE FORMER YUGOSLAVIA.  A SECOND DART FIELD 
OFFICER, J. DORROH, CURRENTLY IN ZENICA, WILL 
JOIN THE INTERAGENCY GROUP IN TUZLA ON APRIL 11. 
DURING THEIR VISIT TO SREBRENICA, THE DART FIELD 
OFFICERS PLAN TO VISIT SREBRENICA IN ORDER TO 
CONDUCT AN ASSESSMENT OF THE HUMANITARIAN 
SITUATION IN THE REGION.  THE DART FIELD OFFICERS 
WILL RETURN TO SPLIT FROM TUZLA ON APRIL 16 AND 
HOPE TO TRAVEL THROUGH ROUTES NOT PREVIOUSLY 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
 
                       UNCLASSIFIED 
 
