WHEAT FLOUR VIA LOZNICA, BANJA KOVILJACA, 
ZVORNIK, CAPARDE, MEMICI, AND KALESIJA.  NO OTHER 
SUCCESSFUL UNHCR CONVOY RUNS WERE REPORTED. 
 
--------------------------------- 
