----------------------------------- 
 
BEFORE THE END OF THE CALENDAR YEAR, WE HOPE TO PRODUCE 
A FRESH LOOK AT PRESIDENT TUDJMAN, PROBABLY IN 
CONNECTION WITH HIS POLITICAL PROSPECTS.  THE REPORT ON 
\"RSK\" LEADERSHIP (PARA 4 ABOVE) WILL INCLUDE SOME 
BIOGRAPHIC ELEMENTS. 
 
------------------------------------ 
