TAGS: War Crimes 
SUBJECT:  Z-4: GOC\'S OBJECTIONS ARE DEEP AND FIRM 
 
 
------- 
SUMMARY 
------- 
 
1.  (LOU)  THE GOC\'S EXPRESSED WILLINGNESS TO 
\"CONSIDER\" THE Z-4 PLAN HAS HELPED CROATIA PRESENT A 
\"REASONABLE\" FACE THAT CONTRASTS FAVORABLY WITH THE 
KRAJINA SERBS\' INTRANSIGENCE.  NEVERTHELESS, CROATIAN 
OBJECTIONS TO VARIOUS ELEMENTS OF THE PLAN ARE DEEPLY 
HELD.  A POINT-BY-POINT REVIEW IN THE HEAVILY 
GOVERNMENT-INFLUENCED \"VJESNIK\" FEBRUARY 1, WHICH 
ESSENTIALLY EVISCERATES ELEMENTS OF THE PLAN, APPEARS 
INDICATIVE.  END SUMMARY. 
 
2. (LOU)  AFTER THE Z-4 GROUP\'S JANUARY 30 PRESENTATION 
OF ITS PLAN FOR POLITICAL REINTEGRATION OF THE SERB- 
CONTROLLED AREAS OF CROATIA, THE CROATIAN GOVERNMENT 
EXPRESSED ITS WILLINGNESS TO REVIEW THE PLAN AND TO 
ACCEPT IT AS A BASIS FOR NEGOTIATION.  IN LIGHT OF THE 
GOC\'S KNOWLEDGE THAT THE \"RSK WOULD FIND THE PLAN 
UNACCEPTABLE EVEN IF IT HAD AGREED TO RECEIVE A COPY OF 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 

 
 
 
 
 
                       LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
PAGE 03        ZAGREB  00454  01 OF 03  011718Z 
IT, THE CROATIAN REACTION WAS UNDOUBTEDLY CRAFTED IN 
PART TO HELP MAINTAIN THE GOC\'S IMAGE OF REASONABLENESS 
AS A SERIOUS PARTNER OF THE \"WEST,\" EXPLORING ALL 
AVENUES TO A PEACEFUL SOLUTION. 
 
3.  (LOU)  THE ORAL REACTIONS OF CROATIAN LEADERS, 
HOWEVER -- BEGINNING BEFORE ACTUAL PRESENTATION WITH 
PRESIDENT TUDJMAN\'S FULMINATIONS ABOUT THE PLAN AND HIS 
EXPRESS HOPE THAT IT WOULD NOT BE PRESENTED TO THE KNIN 
SERBS -- MAKE CLEAR THAT THE CROATS HAVE SERIOUS 
RESERVATIONS ON MANY ASPECTS OF THE Z-4 PLAN, MOST 
RELATING TO ITS PERCEIVED INFRINGEMENTS OF CROATIAN 
SOVEREIGNTY.  AS FM GRANIC TOLD \'DIE WELT,\' THERE 
SHOULD BE NO ELEMENTS OF A \"STATE WITHIN A STATE.\" 
(DETAILS SEPTEL.)  FURTHER, PRESIDENTIAL ADVISER 
SARINIC, AFTER RECEIVING HIS COPY OF THE PLAN, NOT ONLY 
WENT PUBLIC WITH SOME RESERVATIONS, BUT CARPED ABOUT 
THE Z-4 GROUP\'S \"AUTONOMOUSLY NEGOTIATING\" WITH THE 
KRAJINA SERBS. 
 
------------------------------------------ 
AUTHORITATIVE \"VJESNIK\" RIPS INTO THE PLAN 
------------------------------------------ 
 
4. (U)  THE NATIONAL DAILY \"VJESNIK,\" AUTHORITATIVE 
BECAUSE OF ITS FAMILIAL TIES TO THE HDZ, PROVIDED ON 
FEBRUARY 1 AN INITIAL PUBLIC GUIDE TO GOVERNMENT 
THINKING ON CERTAIN UNACCEPTABLE ASPECTS OF THE PLAN. 
THE ARTICLE CARRIES A FULL-PAGE REVIEW OF THE PLAN 
TITLED \"WHAT IS QUESTIONABLE IN THE Z-4 PLAN?\"  MAIN 
POINTS WERE: 
                   LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 

 
 
 
 
 
                       LIMITED OFFICIAL USE 
 
