AUTHORITIES ARE CONSISTENTLY DENYING FUEL CONVOYS 
TO BOSNIAN SERB AND KRAJINA SERB TERRITORY.  THE 
CONVOY OFFICER EXPLAINED THAT THE CROATIAN 
AUTHORITIES WILL OFTEN GIVE CLEARANCE TO THE 
SMALLER FUEL TRUCK, WHICH CAN TRANSPORT 4 MT OF 
FUEL, BUT DENIES CLEARANCE FOR THE 15 MT TANKER. 
 
