OF SUCH ROCKETS REACHING ZAGREB.  SUCH TARGETING WOULD BE 
\"CRAZY,\" MILITARILY INSIGNIFICANT, AND THEREFORE ONLY A 
WAR CRIME. 
 
20.  TOLJ CLAIMED THE HV HAD WANTED TO OPEN TODAY TO 
JOURNALISTS THE ROAD TO KOSTAVICA, WHERE THE HV AND 5TH 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 

 
 
 
 
 
