      SRPP-00  EB-01    ED-01    HHS-01   H-01     SSA-01   TEDE-00 
      INR-00   IO-00    LAB-01   L-01     ADS-00   NSAE-00  NSCE-00 
      OIC-02   PRS-01   P-00     SCT-00   SP-00    STR-00   TRSE-00 
      USIE-00  PRM-10   PRME-01  PRMC-01  DRL-09   G-00       /033W 
