"5471","2/3/2003 12:16","03ZAGREB252","Embassy Zagreb","UNCLASSIFIED","03ZAGREB252","This record is a partial extract of the original cable. The full text of the original cable is not available.


 ","UNCLAS ZAGREB 000252 
 
