BOTH TO SEMNEBY AND THE AMBASSADOR THAT RACAN WILL NOT ENGAGE 
ON IC CONCERNS ANYTIME SOON, IF EVER.  RACAN IS NO LEADER; 
THEREFORE, WE BELIEVE THAT THIS ANTI-COOPERATION 
CONSTELLATION WILL PREVAIL ABSENT CONSTANT AND STRONG IC 
PRESSURE.  WE WILL WORK TO REINFORCE THE PRESSURE HERE.  WE 
URGE THAT THE USG PRESS THIS ISSUE IN BRUSSELS AND IN EU AND 
NATO CAPITALS WHENEVER CROATIA IS ON THE AGENDA.  UNLESS WE 
PRESS THE GOC HARD AND CONSTANTLY, WE WILL NOT GET THE 
FORCEFUL GOC ACTION NEEDED TO GET SIGNIFICANT NUMBERS OF 
RETURNEES HOME, EVER. 
 
