TAGS: PREL, MARR, MOPS, HR, IZ, FR 
SUBJECT: CROATIA APPROVES USE OF AIRSPACE, AIRFIELDS FOR 
CIVAIR TRANSIT OF TROOPS TO MIDEAST 
 
                       CONFIDENTIAL 
 
PAGE 02        ZAGREB  00428  02 OF 02  261353Z 
CROATIAN GOVERNMENT WILL ESTABLISH INTERAGENCY WORKING GROUP 
CONSISTING OF THE FOLLOWING: 
 
- MINISTRY OF DEFENSE, CHAIR 
- MINISTRY OF TRANSPORT, TRAFFIC AND COMMUNICATIONS, MEMBER 
- MINISTRY OF FOREIGN AFFAIRS, MEMBER 
- MINISTRY OF INTERIOR, MEMBER 
- CROATIAN AIR TRAFFIC CONTROL, MEMBER 
 
IV. CROATIAN GOVERNMENT WILL INFORM CROATIAN PARLIAMENT ON 
THE IMPLEMENTATION OF THIS DECISION. 
 
V. THIS DECISION BECOMES EFFECTIVE AS OF THE PROCLAMATION 
DATE AND IT WILL BE PUBLISHED IN THE OFFICIAL GAZETTE. 
 
ZAGREB, 26 FEBRUARY 2003 
PRIME MINISTER 
IVICA RACAN 
END TEXT 
ROSSIN 
 
