EVEN WHICH COULD BE SEEN AS PROVIDING COMPETITION TO DOMESTIC 
FIRMS, WILL COME UNDER ATTACK.  ELECTION YEAR CALCULATIONS 
WILL PROBABLY LEAD TO VERY MARGINAL PROGRESS ON 
PRIVATIZATION, MOUNTING DEBT, AND LOST TIME ON ECONOMIC 
REFORM. 
