SUBJECT: ANOTHER PROBLEM SOLVED? -- CROATIA FLOATS NATIONAL 
STRATEGY FOR ROMA 
 
AND LEFT HER SPEECHLESS: A ROMA NGO LEADER COMPLAINED TO HER 
\"YOU ARE GETTING RICH ON OUR CHILDREN WHEN IT SHOULD BE US 
