STATUS OF THE RAJIC CASE 
------------------------ 

3. (C) THE APRIL 5 ARREST IN SPLIT OF BOSNIAN CROAT ICTY 
FUGITIVE IVICA RAJIC BROUGHT TO A CLOSE AN EIGHT-MONTH 
MANHUNT CONDUCTED BY A SPECIAL UNIT OF THE CROATIAN POLICE 
