"7682","4/28/2003 6:25","03ZAGREB927","Embassy Zagreb","UNCLASSIFIED//FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY","03ZAGREB867|03ZAGREB927","This record is a partial extract of the original cable. The full text of the original cable is not available.

