"13310","1/16/2004 6:18","04ZAGREB85","Embassy Zagreb","UNCLASSIFIED","03ZAGREB2224","This record is a partial extract of the original cable. The full text of the original cable is not available.


 ","UNCLAS  ZAGREB 000085 
 
SIPDIS 
 
 
USDA FOR FAS/OA/BSIMMONS 
 
USDA FOR APHIS/DRS/JTURNER 
 
STATE FOR EB/MTA/ATT 
 
