SUBJECT: CROATIA\'S NEW ICTY PIFWCS DEPART VOLUNTARILY FOR 
THE HAGUE 
 
REF: ZAGREB 380 
 
INFORMATION IS SENSITIVE, BUT UNCLASSIFIED. PLEASE TREAT 
