SUBJECT: CROATIA ARMS CONTROL AND RACVIAC POINTS DELIVERED 
 
REF: A) STATE 201227 B) STATE 20123 C) ZAGREB 1365 
 
1. (U) Poloff delivered refs A & B messages to Drazen 
Hrastic, MFA Head of Cooperative Security Section on Sept. 
21.  Poloff also informed RACVIAC directly of the U.S. 
decision (ref B) to accept observer status on Oct. 11. 
Hrastic welcomed the RACVIAC decision and noted that the 
