first Croatian diplomat assigned to the Croatian contribution 
to the German-led PRT in Afghanistan.  He expects to arrive 
in Afghanistan in early November.  We have found Hrastic to 
be an energetic and able interlocutor on a broad range of 
security, arms control, and non-proliferation issues and 
believe he will make a strong contribution to Croatia\'s 
Afghanistan contingent. 
