"24800","12/30/2004 16:00","04ZAGREB2210","Embassy Zagreb","UNCLASSIFIED","04ZAGREB1571|04ZAGREB1601|04ZAGREB2002","This record is a partial extract of the original cable. The full text of the original cable is not available.

